INSERT IGNORE INTO `posts` (`id`, `author_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `excerpt`, `body`, `image`, `slug`, `meta_title`, `meta_description`, `status`, `featured`, `editor_pick`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `read_time`) VALUES
	(2, 3, NULL, 'Choosing the Right Website Design & Development Company', 'When it comes to website design and development, your website is where visitors get their first impression.', '<p>When it comes to website design and development, your website is where visitors get their first impression.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#factors_choosing">What factors to consider while choosing an agency?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#business_project_requirements">Note down your business project requirements</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#analyze_company">Analyze the company\'s capabilities</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#cost_factor">Cost / value for money factor&nbsp;</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#procedure_deliverables">Know about the procedure and deliverables&nbsp;</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#timeframe_project">Ask about the timeframe for your project</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/June2022/joubi-develop-by-cynosure.webp" alt="Joubi Web Design by Cynosure Designs" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Your online rankings, customer retention and conversion rates all depend on how your site is built. If you are a startup looking for a new website or brand that wants to redesign it, it is obvious to think about how you can get the right company for this particular job. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">Cynosure Designs</a> believes in providing the right information to the clients to help them make the right decision.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="factors_choosing">What factors to consider while choosing an agency?</h2>\r\n<p>So if nothing else, here are some important factors to consider when hiring a <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">website design and development</a> company in the United Kingdom.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="business_project_requirements">Note down your business project requirements.</h3>\r\n<p>The first and the most important element is that you need to make a list of your needs and requirements. Most customers make hasty decisions and go through a process that never ends well. Since it is good to consider a few predetermined changes in design and functionalities, but at the same time, you need to be fully aware of the type of changes you are looking for. Your entire business model can be affected by a minor change in functionality.</p>\r\n<p>A clear vision regarding your goals and objectives can become advantageous and favorable for your business in the long run. Some development platforms are better suited to some businesses, while others can be challenging from a marketing perspective. Take responsibility for your project on your own, and don\'t leave anyone in charge. Additionally, once the website has been delivered to you, you will most likely be responsible for maintaining and managing it. Be sure to choose a development platform that makes it easy for you and your in-house team.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="analyze_company">Analyze the company&rsquo;s capabilities</h3>\r\n<p>The most crucial factor to consider before entrusting your project to a web agency is to know whether they are capable or not to handle and meeting your specific requirements. Some development companies specialize in particular areas, while others have a dynamic portfolio. You can get a good idea from ​​their portfolio of design, development, and content skills. When you\'re at it, don\'t forget to look at the agency\'s success rate and feedback from previous clients. It also gives you a good idea of ​​their potential and technical skills.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="cost_factor">Cost / value for money factor&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>The cost factor is also an important aspect of decision-making for a company. For many people, it all depends on the agency that will get the job done at the lowest cost. Ask the agency what services they cover other than <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">web development and design services</a>. Ask if they will provide support and hosting services within the budget after the project is completed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Compared to well-reputed agencies, you may find significant rate differences between newer agencies with a limited portfolio. This is because the market is full of individual freelancers claiming to be an agency. Still, in reality, they are working to the best of their ability or have a team with limited experience to do it all.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You should always choose a reputable web development company with a proven track record, even if that charges a small extra cost, as your website is a vital asset for your business and determines what kind of brand image you will have for your audience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/June2022/ratchet-develop-by-cynosure.webp" alt="Ratchet shop Ecommerce Develop by Cynosure Designs" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/boost-your-business-multifold-through-an-optimized-ui-ux-design">Boost Your Business Multifold Through An Optimized UI/UX Design</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="procedure_deliverables">Know about the procedure and deliverables&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>Projects are often delayed or even canceled because there is no transparency between companies and clients about the procedure and deliverables. The process and outcomes must be discussed and agreed upon by the agency before the contract is signed to avoid unnecessary delays. Each company has its unique procedure and style of working. All you have to do is determine the fastest route for your project.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="timeframe_project">Ask about the timeframe for your project.</h3>\r\n<p>Identifying and setting the time frame for your project plays a vital role in achieving your milestones and keeping multi-stage projects on track. Deadlines indicate what and when should be expected to be delivered, and you can review your project without confusion. It\'s normal to exceed a deadline by a day or two, but this way, you can not only check how the site is performing along the way but also make sure it\'s done on time. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Contact us</a> for more queries!</p>\r\n<p>Our website has been reviewed and approved by designerlistings.org - <a href="https://www.designerlistings.org/Software-Design-and-Development/C21-1-0.htm">Software Design and Development Listings</a></p>', 'posts/February2022/f7ZpTcVpisun99oTgYX2.jpg', 'choosing-the-absolute-website-design-and-development-company-for-your-business', 'Choosing the absolute Website Design Company for your business', 'Looking for a professional Website Design and Development Agency? Sharing various tips and guidelines in choosing the right company for your business/brand.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-02-10 06:23:00', '2022-08-30 08:22:17', 4),
	(3, 3, NULL, 'Digital Marketing Strategies to grow your business', 'The interactive nature of digital marketing strategies can help companies expand their customers in a short period of time.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#digital_marketing">What actually Digital Marketing is?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#structure_digital_marketing">How to structure a Digital Marketing Strategy?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#plan">Plan</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#reach">Reach</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#act">Act</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#convert">Convert</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#engage">Engage</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#digital_marketing_tactics">What can be the Digital Marketing Tactics?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">Companies that want to learn and adapt to the current business trends may likely reach successful milestones earlier than many others. If you run a small business or own a business and meanwhile managing the digital marketing campaigns on your own, can be difficult and require a lot of effort on your part. But there is always a solution to every problem that needs to be found. Let us offer you a solution that can help you reach the turning point in your online presence and unlock the door to success for your business\' digital growth.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="digital_marketing">What actually Digital Marketing is?</h2>\r\n<p>Digital marketing is the promotion of products or services through various forms of electronic support, based primarily on the Internet. Digital marketing is focused on your entire online marketing exercise. Many companies are already taking advantage of digital marketing over traditional marketing. Unlike traditional marketing, it involves the use of networks and methods to understand the scenario in real-time. This allows organizations to analyze marketing campaigns and take the necessary action. Whatever your business sells, digital marketing can work effectively for any sector. With digital marketing, you can see results much faster than with offline marketing.</p>\r\n<p>The interactive nature of digital marketing strategies can help companies expand their customers in a short period of time. There are four steps to a Successful Digital Marketing strategy:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>SWOT Analysis</li>\r\n<li>SMART Business Goals</li>\r\n<li>Market Segmentation</li>\r\n<li>Build Buyer Personas</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="structure_digital_marketing">How to structure a Digital Marketing Strategy?</h2>\r\n<p>The digital marketing strategy helps in reaching your target audience cost-effectively and measurably with the benefits of increasing brand loyalty and conversion rates. Here we will discuss with you the stages of digital marketing strategies that are considered essential to meet business goals and objectives.</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Plan</li>\r\n<li>Reach</li>\r\n<li>Act</li>\r\n<li>Convert</li>\r\n<li>Engage</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="plan">1- Plan</h3>\r\n<p>Every successful digital marketing strategy starts with a plan! We encourage you to choose a data-based approach, evaluate your current digital marketing effectiveness, and plan for improvements. Multi-channel planning options include customizing analytics, setting up KPI dashboards, and setting SMART goals to create growth priority strategies for deploying digital marketing media, technology, and data to increase leads and sales. For your digital marketing strategy to work effectively and efficiently, we recommend taking a digitally oriented approach to strategy and planning. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk">Cynosure Design\'s</a> digital transformation solutions are designed for marketers and managers to create a fully integrated marketing strategy based on data that supports the overall vision of their business. The goal of digital transformation is to improve the digital maturity of your business while integrating digital marketing activities consistently with the marketing of brands and products within the business. An optimized digital marketing plan includes full enterprise-wide digital marketing integration, a structure testing and optimization program and data integration for 360-degree customer views.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="reach">2- Reach</h3>\r\n<p>Strengthen your marketing funnel by reaching more customers and building knowledge. Present your digital marketing strategy with the latest important online marketing techniques that will increase traffic to your site. Smart Insights members can keep up with the latest marketing techniques at every stage of the strategy Framework. Take a look at the three steps below to improve <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Organic_search_results">organic search</a> in 2022 based on our digital marketing trends.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We continue to check for base updates, as many marketers are already reporting significant differences in traffic from the July 2021 core updates.</li>\r\n<li>Track opportunities from structured data and SERP&rsquo;s features.</li>\r\n<li>It\'s important to optimize changes in keyword behavior due to the increase in local voice queries when targeting local buyers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/how-to-reach-the-right-audience-with-digital-marketing">How to Reach the Right Audience with Digital Marketing</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="act">3- Act</h3>\r\n<p>Encourage interactions on your website or social media platforms to help you generate leads in the future. Once you reach your audience, it\'s important that you influence their next steps to the purchasing decision.</p>\r\n<p>is where strategic content marketing comes into play. Use <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Content_marketing">content marketing</a> to create, inspire, educate and persuade potential converters throughout their customer lifecycle. You need to look at today\'s wide range of interactive design innovations that demonstrably increase engagement with your content.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="convert">4- Convert</h3>\r\n<p>Of course, the peak of your structured digital marketing strategy is the conversion of more customers. Use retargeting, support, and conversion rate optimization to remind your audience and convince them to shop online or offline when phone and in-person channels are important to you.</p>\r\n<p>Following key analytics show the popularity of social e-commerce:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>87% of e-commerce shoppers believe that social media can help them make purchasing decisions.</li>\r\n<li>1 in 4 business owners sell via <a href="https://www.facebook.com/">Facebook</a>.</li>\r\n<li>40% of entrepreneurs use social media to generate sales.</li>\r\n<li>30% of consumers say they shop directly through social media platforms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="engage">5- Engage</h3>\r\n<p>After working hard for conversion rates, did you know that you can increase sales by existing customers by engaging them after their first purchase? Enhance your personalized communication with web, email, and <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">Social Media Marketing</a> with the data you already have about them to create hyper personalized marketing campaigns.</p>\r\n<p>Options for researching and testing customer engagement for digital marketers today include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Customer persons</li>\r\n<li>Customer paths and content mapping</li>\r\n<li>Voice in customer surveys</li>\r\n<li>Path analysis</li>\r\n<li>Website customer surveys</li>\r\n<li>Usability studies of digital experiences</li>\r\n<li>Multidimensional testing</li>\r\n<li>Insights into consumer behavior</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>View the list of <a href="https://www.designrush.com/agency/digital-agencies/uk/london" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Digital Agencies in London</strong></a> by DesignRush</p>\r\n<h2 id="digital_marketing_tactics">What can be the Digital Marketing Tactics?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class="table table-bordered table-responsive">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</strong><br />Rank the business Website higher in Google search engine results.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Pay Per Click (PPC)</strong><br />Rank the business Website higher in Google search engine results.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Social Media Marketing (SMM)</strong><br />Promoting brand/business on social media channels.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Content Marketing</strong><br />Increase brand awareness by storytelling and information sharing.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Email Marketing</strong><br />Where recipients click and open the link in the email.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Mobile Marketing</strong><br />Target audience through mobile applications, emails, social media etc</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information contact our <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Digital Marketers</a> who will assist you in meeting your needs and requirements.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/5-major-tips-to-launch-an-effective-digital-marketing-campaign">5 major Tips to Launch an Effective Digital Marketing Campaign</a></p>', 'posts/February2022/49WYuqmZGybJ4kKne1AM.jpg', 'digital-marketing-strategies-to-grow-your-business', 'Latest Digital Marketing strategies to grow your business', 'Want your business to grow? Sharing various adaptable Digital Marketing Strategies and Marketing Trends to boost your business.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-02-10 07:29:00', '2022-08-18 10:56:22', 5),
	(4, 3, NULL, 'How to Reach the Right Audience with Digital Marketing', 'Digital Marketing should always contact the right audience at the right place at the right time', '<p>Digital Marketing should always contact the right audience at the right place at the right time. Targeting the right people for your brand is extremely important for your business to grow.</p>\r\n<p><br /><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/June2022/how-to-reach-the-right-audience.webp" alt="Traffic Preview Of a Site on a TAB" /></p>\r\n<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#target_audience">What is Target Audience?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#considerable_audience">What are the considerable Audience Characteristics?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#how_to_target_audience">How to Target the Right Audience with Digital Marketing?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#business_offers">Understand What Your Business Offers.</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#audience_persona">Identify Your Audience Persona.</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#organic_keywords">Learn about your Organic Keywords</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#retargeting_customers">Retargeting your Customers</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>If you find the right audience and access, you can adjust the messages to attract the specific area, which increases the likelihood of attracting attention.</p>\r\n<p>Many companies find this element essential for the effectiveness and smooth running of the campaign. Therefore, the market study budget is important to choose for a large part of the functionality.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>According to the <a href="https://www.forbes.com/?sh=76bca802254c">Forbes</a> Insights report, 43% of companies spend more than half their budget on achieving a particular goal, and 84% expect investment to increase in the coming years.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="target_audience">What is Target Audience?</h2>\r\n<p>In the world of digital marketing, effective campaigns don\'t reach everyone. To develop an effective digital marketing campaign, <strong>you need to get people who take advantage of what you offer.</strong> The people in this group are called the target audience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="considerable_audience">What are the considerable Audience Characteristics?</h2>\r\n<p>There are many traits to consider when building the image of your target audience. Here are some characteristics that may affect their level of interest in your business.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Age</li>\r\n<li>Location</li>\r\n<li>Gender</li>\r\n<li>Budget</li>\r\n<li>Income level</li>\r\n<li>Interests</li>\r\n<li>Internet search history</li>\r\n<li>Prior purchases</li>\r\n<li>Marital status</li>\r\n<li>Internet device</li>\r\n<li>Religion</li>\r\n<li>And more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="how_to_target_audience">How to Target the Right Audience with Digital Marketing?</h2>\r\n<p>Carefully read the steps below to help you reach the right online target audience for your digital marketing campaign.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="business_offers">Understand What Your Business Offers.</h3>\r\n<p>Knowing your product or service is the first step in identifying who you are targeting. Who benefits more from what you provide? What are the unique features of your product? Is your product cost-effective? If you answer these questions, you will understand the outcomes of your digital marketing efforts.</p>\r\n<p>If you are already running your company, you can easily analyze the best customers&rsquo; interests and characteristics to identify a marketing strategy. Your best customer common traits and concerns about the particular products or services will be able to match the existing marketing strategy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="audience_persona">Identify Your Audience Persona.</h3>\r\n<p>Google Analytics and the search console can tell you what is important to the audience and how and what people do to our store upon arrival. Advertising managers and Facebook Insights can show us the customers\' age, position, location, interest, and behaviour. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">Social media</a> tools can tell what customers think of our products and what other topics are attractive to them.</p>\r\n<p>Use these tools to determine better ideas about the demographic profiles of your audience to understand what is most important and interesting for them. Several tools easily integrate with Bigcommerce to help you in this area. These tools use your business and connected account information and then forward ads to bring more customers to your website.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/June2022/traffic-preview-of-a-site.webp" alt="Traffic Preview Of a Site on Papers" width="1000" height="668" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="organic_keywords">Learn about your Organic Keywords</h3>\r\n<p>Organic search is usually the biggest source of traffic for any website. It is important not only to understand the terms people bring to your store but also why those terms are being used.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Keywords are usually divided into three main categories:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Informational Keywords - Used to find a wide variety of topics and items</li>\r\n<li>Navigational Keywords - Used to find specific websites or products</li>\r\n<li>Transactional Keywords - Used to find the product to be purchased</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>By identifying your search terms and related users, you can develop content to better understand your demands for your audience. Useful content is often found in post blogs, FAQs or resource sections.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can use tools to check if other websites are already leading for your search terms. These platforms show the number of backlinks, publisher, publication date, and more. Find out a little about what your competitors and the most successful foreign brands are doing, then rebuild with your own brand style.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="retargeting_customers">Retargeting your Customers</h3>\r\n<p>If a customer comes to your store early on their shopping journey through a blog post, display advertisement, or other media, they\'re unlikely to make a shopping visit there. This is predictable and good. You can consider them and bring those customers back to your store by trying to re-target them. 70% of the visitors are retargeted and converted with display ads.</p>\r\n<p>You can use several digital channels to run your campaigns smoothly. Similarly, AdWords, Google Display ads, or <a href="https://www.facebook.com">Facebook</a> are the mediums for retargeting. After understanding your customers and their traits, use digital channels to reach that audience, drive quality traffic, improve on-site engagement, and, most importantly, increase sales. If you are looking to expand your business online, you can hire a <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Social Media Marketing agency</a> to help you in your business growth.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/6-most-effective-digital-marketing-methods-to-grow-your-local-business" target="_blank" rel="noopener">6 Most Effective Digital Marketing Methods To Grow Your Local Business.</a></p>', 'posts/June2022/gNzbbcNTqiQ5lq0mcEk4.webp', 'how-to-reach-the-right-audience-with-digital-marketing', 'How to Reach the Right Audience with Digital Marketing', 'How to reach the right audience with Digital Marketing in this modern era? Sharing various adaptable Digital Marketing tactics to increase your brand awareness.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-02-10 07:54:00', '2022-08-05 10:31:27', 4),
	(5, 3, NULL, '5 A\'s of successful Digital Marketing Transformation', 'The ability to be efficient, fast, and able to adapt to stay on top with design and technology globally.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_are_5a_role">What are 5 A\'s and their role in the digital transformation journey?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#audience_heading">Audience </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#assets_heading">Assets</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#access_heading">Access</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#attribution_heading">Attribution</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#automation_heading">Automation</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#conclusion_heading">Conclusion</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>\r\n<p>The digital marketing revolution aims to move from digital complacency to actively seeking digital excellence through adequately optimizing your digital channels. It simply means being efficient, fast, and able to adapt to stay on top of design and technology globally. The processes, systems, and organizational structures that work against these goals are significant in why some digital transformation initiatives fail.</p>\r\n<p>Building on our collective over the digitally transforming companies is undergoing a simplified framework. This framework outlines the four pillars of digital transformation we are witnessing today: IT improvement, digitization operations, digital marketing, and digital business. These four factors are part of most businesses\' successful digital transformation journey.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="what_are_5a_role">What are 5 A\'s and their role in the digital transformation journey?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To address the shortfalls and help businesses to grasp the fundamentals of digital transformation, Cynosure Designs have put together the five major fundamental principles, called <strong>5 A\'s</strong>.</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Audience</li>\r\n<li>Assets</li>\r\n<li>Access</li>\r\n<li>Attribution</li>\r\n<li>Automation</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="audience_heading">1- Audience: recognize and engage the right people</h3>\r\n<p>A brand that understands its audience is more likely to grab their attention. However, the challenge for marketers is to organize their data sources to identify, understand and interact with potential customers. To give yourself the best chance of doing so, follow these three simple steps:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Combine online and offline customer data to get a unified view of your audience across all channels.</li>\r\n<li>Centralize, evaluate and Consolidate your available data into a single tool to segment customers, and understand their intent, purchase journey, and long-term value.</li>\r\n<li>Determine a targeting strategy for the brand to reach your audience anywhere on the shopping trip and in all related media (video, show, search, offline).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br /><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/July2022/target-audience.webp" alt="Target Audience image on laptop" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read More:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/how-to-reach-the-right-audience-with-digital-marketing">How to Reach the Right Audience with Digital Marketing</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="assets_heading">2- Assets: providing the compatible user experience</h3>\r\n<p>After identifying and finding the right audience, you must deliver a compelling customer experience. The challenge for brands is to create equally engaging, compelling experiences across all digital touchpoints (websites, apps, social networks, digital advertising) and real life (at the point of sale, during events).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Emphasize simplicity, speed, and convenience in all your channels and messages. In other words, eliminate the friction points in the customer journey, especially on mobile devices.</li>\r\n<li>Produce relevant and context-sensitive ads using audience insights and channel knowledge, and ensure you pick the suitable medium and format for your advertising. For example, the kind of message you convey during a 6-second video ad should be different from a longer-form video ad or banner.</li>\r\n<li>Enrich the user experience with relevant data. Combine your data with audience indicators (search, display, and YouTube for the Google Network) to understand your audience\'s intent and behavior and tailor your ads accordingly.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="access_heading">3- Access: increase the reach of your messages to the audience</h3>\r\n<p>If you want to reach your prospects wherever they are on the buying journey, you will have to consider the scope and inventory. And as long as costs are under control, you should have access to as much available inventory as possible. New tools are available to give you a complete view of your media investments to manage contact frequency better, ensure maximum transparency on all media purchases across channels, and meet brand safety standards.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="attribution_heading">4- Attribution: consider each medium of contact</h3>\r\n<p>The attribution model that accounts for the dynamics between channels and devices by analyzing the shopping spree and allocating the appropriate credit allows for much more accurate and meaningful budget decisions. With time, multichannel purchases are increasing. It\'s tough to decide where and how to focus your efforts when you have multiple choices of channels and types of customers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="automation_heading">5- Automation: improving performance by automating operations</h3>\r\n<p>Automation is not just a long way to cut costs, but it also delivers consistent, helpful, and personalized customer experiences at scale and generates significant revenue benefits.</p>\r\n<p>Digital marketing campaigns create massive amounts of data that can become overwhelming instantly. Machine learning technology can automate prominent keywords, bids, creative assets, targeting, and attribution.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/July2022/digital-transformation.webp" alt="Digital Transformation" /></p>\r\n<h2 id="conclusion_heading">Conclusion</h2>\r\n<p>Audience, Assets, Access, Attribution, and Automation are the 5 New pillars that can help you become a master of digital transformation, delivering rich customer experiences and improved business outcomes.</p>\r\n<p>Digital Marketing transformation is the shift in organizational thinking from traditional marketing channels to digital media.</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Contact us</a> for more information!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Read:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/5-major-tips-to-launch-an-effective-digital-marketing-campaign">5 major Tips to Launch an Effective Digital Marketing Campaign</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/February2022/wgCe5c5nDwDnlZj2jaz7.jpg', '5-a-s-of-successful-digital-marketing-transformation', '5 A\'s of successful Digital Marketing Transformation | Cynosure Designs', 'What are the 5 "A" s of successful Digital Marketing Transformation in this modern era? Sharing adaptable Marketing Trends to increase your brand awareness.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-02-10 08:07:00', '2022-07-04 07:00:35', 5),
	(6, 3, NULL, 'Logo Defines Your Brand', 'A logo is a trademark of a brand or a company that represents every aspect of it.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#must_have_logo">What a Logo must-have?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#why_logo_needed">Why does your Business need a Logo?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#trending_logo">What are the trending Logos in the Business Market?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#monogram_heading">Monogram Logos/Lettermarks</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#logo_types">Wordmarks/Logotypes</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#pictorial_marks">Pictorial marks (or logo symbols) </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#mascots">Mascots</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#combination_mark">The combination mark</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#the_emblem">The emblem</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_words">Final Words</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>\r\n<p>A logo is a trademark of a brand or a company that represents every aspect of it. Many designs and techniques can be used to create a logo. Logo design is a combination of old and new trends and if you are looking for a custom logo design company, Cynosure Designs strives to provide the designs you want.</p>\r\n<p>Let\'s get a few things straight: your logo and your website are not your brands. Your brand is the culmination of the experience, vision, and reputation that people have at your service. Branding is the activity taken to build your brand (strategy). And brand identity is the expression of your brand (logo, typography, color, etc.).</p>\r\n<p>It is worth mentioning that there is no right and wrong way of developing logos and brands. Design and idea generation is an organic process and all of us have our ways of getting to the finish line.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="must_have_logo">What a Logo must have?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>There are some basic features that a logo should have at its core.</li>\r\n<li>First of all, the logo must be immediately recognizable.</li>\r\n<li>The logo must be clear and easy to interpret to connect with your audience</li>\r\n<li>Most importantly logo must be simple so it works across multiple media platforms</li>\r\n<li>The logo needs to communicate who you are and what you do in an instant</li>\r\n<li>The logo needs simple colors, great typography, and strong visual element</li>\r\n<li>Logo design must be versatile.</li>\r\n<li>It must be able to personify your brand</li>\r\n<li>and ultimately, the logo must be timeless.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If the logo of your choice meets all these requirements, you have everything you need.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="why_logo_needed">Why does your Business need a Logo?</h2>\r\n<p>As said, your logo is important to your business because it expresses ownership, quality, and value. It is published on your products, your business card, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">website design</a>, social media networks, and especially in the minds of your clients.</p>\r\n<p>Your logo is probably one of the first interactions with people and this is your chance to make a strong first impression, show you that you provide quality service, and visually express your goal. The logo plays a vital role that any business can own, and no single design or piece will mean more to a business\'s profile or public image.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="trending_logo">What are the trending Logos in the Business Market?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Monogram Logos/Lettermarks</li>\r\n<li>Wordmarks/Logotypes</li>\r\n<li>Pictorial marks (or logo symbols)</li>\r\n<li>Mascots</li>\r\n<li>The combination mark</li>\r\n<li>The emblem</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="monogram_heading">Monogram Logos/Lettermarks</h3>\r\n<p>The logos consist of letters, usually the brand initials that represent simplicity and brand identification. CNN, HP, IBM, and HBO have strong typography-based logos.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="logo_types">Wordmarks/Logotypes</h3>\r\n<p>The font-based logo consists of the &ldquo;business name&rdquo; itself. Think of VISA, GOOGLE, and COCA-COLA logos that focus on the brand name and create a strong image.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="pictorial_marks">Pictorial Marks/Logo Symbols&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>A graphics-based logo or an icon is strong brand recognition. When it comes to the iconic APPLE logo and the TWITTER logo, they represent the true brand mark and are only the image.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\r\n<h3 id="mascots">Mascot Logos</h3>\r\n<p>The logos involve an illustrated character or sometimes a cartoonish image that creates your brand spokesperson. Famous mascots include KFC&rsquo;s Colonel, Kool-Aid Man, and Planters Mr. Peanuts which are appealing to families and children.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="combination_mark">Combination Mark</h3>\r\n<p>The logo is the combination of a wordmark or letter mark, pictorial mark, abstract mark, or mascot. Composing the picture and the text side-by-side or integrating them to create an image. Some well known combination mark logos include Doritos, Burger King, and Lacoste.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="the_emblem">The Emblem</h3>\r\n<p>An Emblem logo consists of a font inside a symbol, icon, or badge, that has a striking impact. The most famous logo designs of Starbucks and Harley-Davidson have a classic stylish appearance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_words">Final Words</h2>\r\n<p>Design matters and you need it! Especially if you want people to give you money and tell the world about you. When you invest in your brand, you give your small business the strength to grow.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Do you have a question about branding or logo design? <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Talk to us</a> if you need a professional logo for your business from our experts at Cynosure Designs.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Your logo is the visual foundation of your brand identity!</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong>&nbsp;<a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/the-top-3-ux-design-trends-for-2022">The Top 3 UX Design Trends for 2022</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/February2022/RHskZvXhTBnJjPXdINLu.jpg', 'logo-defines-your-brand', 'Innovative logo Describes Your Brand | Cynosure Designs', 'What is the importance of Logo Design in a business? Sharing key factors about why, how, and what type of Logo a business needs in the competitive market.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-02-10 08:17:00', '2022-07-04 08:16:13', 5),
	(7, 3, NULL, 'Boost your Business Multifold through an Optimized UI/UX Design', 'Having an optimized UI/UX is paramount to getting greater traffic influx and conversions.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#improve_your_ui">So what can you do to improve your UI/UX?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#mobile_responsiveness">Mobile Responsiveness</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#the_content">The Content</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#audience_shoes">Put yourself in your Audience&rsquo;s Shoes</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_words">Final Words</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">While the digital landscape has evolved massively since the pandemic, with more businesses turning to digital transformation, many are struggling to stay afloat amidst the overwhelming competition they have in their particular domains. That said, if you are among such businesses, you could still make it big in the digital arena, provided you keep up with the contemporary trends in eCommerce. What good is your website if it&rsquo;s sitting at the bottom of the pile? A staggering 95% of the people don&rsquo;t make it past the first page of the search engine when looking up a service or a product. So how do you climb up the ranks and get more traffic influx? The answer is your <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>When was the last time you went to an ecommerce website and ended up abandoning the purchase simply because the process was too lengthy or complicated? That&rsquo;s exactly what happens when you have a poor UI/UX. It does more than make you lose a few potential customers and also translates into a higher bounce rate which ultimately prompts the search engine to bury you under the tons of competition you have in the market.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="improve_your_ui">So what can you do to improve your UI/UX?</h2>\r\n<p>Optimized UI/UX is paramount to getting a more significant traffic influx and conversions. Here are the top factors that contribute to an optimized <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">website design</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="mobile_responsiveness">Mobile Responsiveness</h2>\r\n<p>If your website design is not mobile responsive, you are missing out on a big chunk of traffic captured by your competitors. <a href="http://www.google.com/">Google</a> is negatively marking you for not entertaining the people searching from mobile devices. Google rolled out its mobile-first indexing policy in 2019, keeping in view that mobile traffic would soon surpass desktop traffic. According to the latest study by Statista, a staggering 54.8% of the global web traffic is coming in through mobile devices. So if you have not already, make your website mobile responsive for better online rankings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="the_content">The Content</h2>\r\n<p>Like it or not, quality content still holds the throne in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_marketing">online marketing</a>. What makes your content stand out when millions of other websites offer similar information about a specific product or service? It mostly boils down to how detailed, informative and well-sorted it is. The last thing you want is for your visitors to be entangled in unnecessary information they have no use for.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="audience_shoes">Put yourself in your Audience&rsquo;s Shoes.</h2>\r\n<p>Understanding the user intent is the essential aspect of any website design. Knowing what your user wants when visiting a particular page can make a difference. For instance, if a user is looking to buy something, it would be unwise to greet them with lengthy content and not show the product. Similarly, if a user is at the top of the funnel and is in the research phase, they are just not ready to bombard by your special discount offers. A little due Diligence would go a long way.</p>\r\n<p>It is very much possible that you have played all the right cards but are still far behind your competitors, and that&rsquo;s because they are doing something that you are not. Doing some industry research early on can save you a lot of trouble. It would help to know what your competitors sitting right up at the top are doing differently.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_words">Final Words</h2>\r\n<p>As much as we wish, there isn&rsquo;t a universal solution in website design. Yet, it is one thing that has the potential to make you an industry leader or irrelevant amongst the growing competition online. Offering a seamless experience to your users sure sounds easy, but there is a lot more to it than meets the eye, which is why you need a <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">professional UI/UX agency</a> to make your design stand out. Whether you are looking to get a new business website or want to revamp your existing one, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">Cynosure Designs</a> is a one-click solution to all your design requirements.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/the-top-3-ux-design-trends-for-2022">The Top 3 UX Design Trends for 2022</a></p>', 'posts/February2022/IhXMBVFVVxOE7x7lnZfg.jpg', 'boost-your-business-multifold-through-an-optimized-ui-ux-design', 'Boost your business through an optimized UI/UX Design', 'Providing essential guidelines to boost your business multifold through an optimized UI/UX design of your website in this digital era.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-02-10 08:43:00', '2022-07-25 09:56:11', 3),
	(8, 3, NULL, '5 major Tips to Launch an Effective Digital Marketing Campaign', 'In today\'s world, effective digital marketing campaigns are essential to increase your audience and brand awareness', '<p>5 major Tips to Launch an Effective Digital Marketing Campaign</p>\r\n<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#5_tips">What are the top 5 tips for launching an Effective Digital Marketing Campaign to level your business?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#compain_goals">Determine your Campaign Goals</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#target_audience">Understand your Target Audience</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#competitor_analysis">Execute Competitor Analysis</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#creative_content">Come up with the Creative Content</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#customer_interaction">Customer Interaction is the Key Factor</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p id="overview">In today\'s world, effective digital marketing campaigns are essential to increase your audience and brand awareness. If you don\'t have a significant online presence, your business may not exist. Digital marketing campaigns have many parts that are essential to their overall success. It\'s important not only to focus individually on each of these areas but also to understand how they work together to ensure the success of your campaign. Your web presence is a valuable tool because billions of people worldwide search for and interact with your online business. Digital marketing for your business means reaching hundreds of customers in seconds. That\'s why real-world digital marketing campaigns make your business stand out.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="5_tips">What are the top 5 tips for launching an Effective Digital Marketing Campaign to level your business?</h2>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">Cynosure Designs</a> shared these top five tips to keep in mind when creating your digital marketing campaign, adequate for your business/brand.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="compain_goals">1- Determine your Campaign Goals</h2>\r\n<p>This section will help you to create the basics of your <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">digital marketing</a> campaign, outlining whatever you want to achieve from your campaign. While making goals, it is necessary to determine the benchmarks for success and campaign limitations. You will also need to create messages and try to promote your digital marketing campaign. Some of the successful marketing campaigns are:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Social Media Marketing</li>\r\n<li>Blogging</li>\r\n<li>Website</li>\r\n<li>SEO Marketing</li>\r\n<li>Email Marketing</li>\r\n<li>Paid Media Marketing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="target_audience">2- Understand your Target Audience</h2>\r\n<p>It is crucial to determine your target audience to pick up your marketing campaign. If you do not know your target group, you will lead a waste of time and money, and if you can create a campaign with your targeted audience, that will be more successful. Use data on the audience\'s demographics and behaviour. Take into account the target group and their profile information such as age, sex and geographical location. It is also essential to know about the audience\'s purchasing habits and communication style. Social media advertisement gives you access to many users that match your target audience\'s niche. These ads can also be affordable and provide essential reach and response rate data.</p>\r\n<p>Consider your target audience and their unique needs to create the most effective campaigns. What problems can you solve for them? Think of your marketing in terms of the target audience to make your message more effective and how your products and services help their lifestyle?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="competitor_analysis">3- Execute Competitor Analysis</h2>\r\n<p>Markets are highly competitive, and online marketing is often saturated. Performing a comprehensive competitor analysis is essential to your marketing campaign. This can give you a good idea of ​​which strategy will work for you and also helps determine which marketing tools can be implemented more.</p>\r\n<p>Engaging with social media is essential for the success of your digital marketing campaigns. Find out how often your competitors share posts and compare the number of likes and comments for posts on your Page. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_media">Social media</a> is a great place to start a comparison. The number of users who like your competitor\'s Page can give you an idea of ​​how your growth compares to others in your industry. Focus on the most successful brands in increasing their audience and think about the strategies they use to increase brand awareness.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="creative_content">4- Come up with the Creative Content</h2>\r\n<p>There is a lot of freedom for creativity in today\'s internet world. Most people with online access are exposed to many advertisements daily. That\'s why your marketing campaign should be prominent.</p>\r\n<p>Make sure you add unique and creative content that matches well with your audience. Do something that grabs attention, whether it be a video, photo or gif. Today\'s average consumer is running out of time. Keep your content light, textured and engaging! Use bold titles and short sentences to catch the eye with attractive taglines and <a href="http://best-hashtags.com/">hashtags</a> to gain attention.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="customer_interaction">5- Customer Interaction is the Key Factor</h2>\r\n<p>When creating a campaign, remember that your customers can interact with you. Your business may receive various questions about the campaign. This is your chance to build a great relationship with your audience and create a great customer experience.</p>\r\n<p>Plus, it\'s a great way to research your audience. Following up on their FAQs can help you better understand their wants and needs. Keep your visitors interested and actively communicate with you. Follow-up is necessary because customers often get distracted and leave the site without purchasing or committing to the product. Provide the additional information they need and ask them about what benefits they are looking for in your product.</p>\r\n<p><strong>BETTER MARKETING, BETTER RETURN ON INVESTMENT!</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/5-digital-marketing-trends-to-be-on-the-lookout-for-in-2022">5 digital marketing trends to be on the lookout for in 2022</a></p>', 'posts/February2022/DQLK53eKPynWZ7LyAOXH.jpg', '5-major-tips-to-launch-an-effective-digital-marketing-campaign', 'Tips to Launch an Effective Digital Marketing Campaign', 'Providing 5 major tips to launch effective Digital Marketing Campaigns that would gain audience attention and increase brand awareness.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-02-11 07:44:00', '2022-07-25 09:54:06', 4),
	(9, 4, NULL, 'What can a digital marketing company do for your business in two steps?', 'Let us tell you in two points how digital marketing can help you in a higher ROI.', '<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#history">History of digital marketing </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#tell_your_customers">Tell your customers that you exist</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#keep_track">Keep track of your customer&rsquo;s actions</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="history">Digital marketing came into existence back in the 1990s with the development of the Web 1.0 platform. This platform allowed users to search but they couldn\'t share anything. Have you ever anticipated it being catapulted this far? Well, nobody did!</p>\r\n<p>Let us tell you in two points how digital marketing can help you in a higher ROI.</p>\r\n<p>Without having to invest a lot of money or time assembling an in-house team, digital marketing services may help you accelerate the ROI of your marketing effort. In this article, we\'ll discuss what a digital marketing firm can do to help you <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/marketing-strategy">perform better</a>, especially what services you can presume they manage for you.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="tell_your_customers">Tell Your Customers That You Exist</h2>\r\n<p>Well, you might think that prior to <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing">digital marketing</a>, businesses were running successfully and they were getting recognized in the market without any digital appearance. People didn\'t have smart devices to waste their time with back then. People would just watch TV, read a newspaper, or glance at billboards to pass the time on their route to another town or city. This is how they would know about a brand&rsquo;s new branch nearby or about a new product.</p>\r\n<p>In today&rsquo;s world where people are always on their phones, scrolling up and down swapping applications, their immediate source of information is digital media. Whatever they learn or get informed about is through digital media. So, reaching out to them through digital media is the foremost technique. But you must be wondering how to do that. Well, this is what a digital marketing company is for.</p>\r\n<p>They will help your business to get recognized by your potential customers using different tools and techniques that they are proficient in. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">Social media marketing</a>, email marketing, search engine optimization, sponsored advertising, and/or influencer marketing are examples of various strategies.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="keep_track">Keep Track Of Your Customers\' Actions</h2>\r\n<p>Previously, the best an advertisement company could do was, transmit your business motto to your clients or display what you are doing in your business through billboards or TV advertisements. But now, you can know as a business owner how many of the customers have seen your message or how many of the clients are interested in buying what you are selling. Doesn\'t that sound interesting to you?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>But wait, what are you going to do with this information? Well, if a company knows what its consumers want, it can promptly manufacture what sells. Knowing the demand before launching anything is a major hit for the firm, and the likelihood of larger revenue is higher than that of unknown demand by clients.</p>\r\n<p>This is not the end, the services are as extensive as <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">digital marketing</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So, what are you waiting for? <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Let&rsquo;s talk about it now!</a></p>', 'posts/February2022/a73kHWSO6ZJ9yBoIKLNR.jpg', 'what-can-a-digital-marketing-company-do-for-your-business-in-two-steps', 'Digital Marketing in two steps | Cynosure Designs', 'Digital marketing came into existence back in the 1990s with the development of the Web 1.0 platform', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-02-15 10:18:00', '2022-07-26 08:58:59', 2),
	(10, 3, NULL, '6 Most Effective Digital Marketing Methods To Grow Your Local Business', 'It\'s important to get involved in digital marketing to attract more local clients.', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#search_engine_optimization">Search Engine Optimization</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#content_marketing">Content Marketing</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#youtube_ads">Youtube Ads</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#facebook_ads">Facebook Advertisements</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#insta_ads">Instagram Ads</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#email_marketing">Email Marketing</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>\r\n<p>If you have a local business, getting involved in digital marketing is essential to attract more local clients. However, with today\'s online advertising opportunities, it\'s easier than ever to target an audience in your area and help them learn about your business. Digital marketing is essential if you want your business to be successful. From helping to attract new customers to increasing sales, the right digital marketing strategy can take your business to new heights.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Here are six ways to grow your local business through digital marketing.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Search Engine Optimization</li>\r\n<li>Content marketing</li>\r\n<li>Youtube Ads</li>\r\n<li>Facebook Advertisements</li>\r\n<li>Instagram Ads</li>\r\n<li>Email marketing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="search_engine_optimization">Search Engine Optimization</h2>\r\n<p>Website optimization will improve your company\'s online presence. SEO is vital in improving the quality and quantity of website traffic to a website or a web page from search engines. Search Engine Optimization is the most practical and effective way to understand customers and reach them, as it provides the best way to understand the voice of the consumers. However, it is a long-term strategy and ultimately increases engagement, traffic and conversion rates by building trust and credibility.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="content_marketing">Content marketing</h2>\r\n<p>Content marketing can also help with SEO rankings. This content describes adding blog posts to your company\'s website to rank higher and attract local customers. The content you create communicates your message, educates your readers, and persuades them to buy your products and services ahead of the competition. Content marketing plays a vital role in achieving business goals such as brand recognition, audience engagement and lead generation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/July2022/content-marketing.webp" alt="content is king on mobile" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Read More:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/5-major-tips-to-launch-an-effective-digital-marketing-campaign">5 Major Tips To Launch An Effective Digital Marketing Campaign</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="youtube_ads">Youtube Ads</h2>\r\n<p>YouTube ads can also appeal to your audience. They are the most effective form of paid traffic because they leverage a user\'s search history with Google\'s artificial intelligence. Google recommends this because AI sends a message to an entire audience for a fraction of the cost of <a href="https://ads.google.com/intl/en_uk/home/">Google AdWords</a>, which means higher ROI for your business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="facebook_ads">Facebook Advertisements</h2>\r\n<p>Many local businesses use <a href="https://www.facebook.com/business/ads">Facebook ads</a> because it\'s easy to create a target audience on the site. However, the sales funnel included in advertising should optimize conversions. Facebook ads cannot fix the bad funnel - they\'re just improving the results you already have. If your funnel does not convert, you will be wasting money. Try different paths with a small audience, and then make changes before spending your entire marketing budget.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="insta_ads">Instagram Ads</h2>\r\n<p>Instagram is still the perfect place to connect with customers in your area with features such as location tags and hashtags in your city or state. From here, you can reach potential customers with large followers and offer them a free product or service in exchange for an Instagram story or post. You need to bring <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">social media</a> back into the human experience - being honest and connecting with other companies on social media can help build a real community. To get started, plug your city into the Locations tab and see which small businesses are popping up.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<h2 id="email_marketing">Email marketing</h2>\r\n<p>Engaging in email marketing today is a great way to retain your customers. There are several creative ways to create an email list for your customers. Above all, email marketing allows you to build relationships with potential customers and past customers. You can have the opportunity to chat with them directly in their inbox at a time that suits them. Combined with the right messages, email can be one of your most influential marketing channels.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/July2022/social-media-marketing.webp" alt="person drawing Social Media Marketing" width="1600" height="900" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>The best way to build a brand is to build an identification in the marketing world. Investing in marketing campaigns will increase your visibility, build a brand name, and gain a competitive edge. This will help you attract new clients and increase the ROI for your business. If you want to help benefit your company with digital marketing, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">speak to us</a> today without hesitation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Everything you need to Grab the Audience\'s Attention</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/5-digital-marketing-trends-to-be-on-the-lookout-for-in-2022">5 Digital Marketing Trends To Be On The Lookout For In 2022</a></p>', 'posts/July2022/fZ6sszXXI81Ws2Q0SR27.webp', '6-most-effective-digital-marketing-methods-to-grow-your-local-business', '6 Effective Digital Marketing Methods | Cynosure Designs', 'From helping to attract new customers to increase sales, the right digital marketing strategy can take your business to new heights.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-03-04 07:41:00', '2022-07-04 05:50:18', 2),
	(11, 3, NULL, 'Magento Versions to build your E-Commerce Business', 'Magento is an open source e-commerce platform that provides customers with a multi-channel experience.', '<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 17pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Overview</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-431f0dac-7fff-b9e6-a255-b346fed7d789" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Magento was first released in 2008 and is an open source e-commerce platform written in PHP that provides your customers with a multi-channel experience. It uses many other PHP frameworks, such as Laminas and Symfony.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cynosure Designs will help you find your way around and will give you an overview of the different methods and versions of Magenta that can be used to build an online store.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 24pt; padding: 24pt 0pt 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 17pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2 Basic Methods for Magento Website Development&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Build a new Magento website from scratch</span></li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Migrate from a different ecommerce platform to Magento.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/MSKMCvXGf3UzjGaKhq93CCgPqa8qjguxhfXNnx6VJGnGgPHG_5hRKLyBZyvQCRPBPKg2UTbxWfcz-lWANd8qqeDm-U_d-oS5WGYqvc1Zw3xCyxqX0FadeojcxmLuREecKbhfGfz1" width="624" height="403" /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 17pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cynosure Designs helps Businesses with supporting versions, Magento 1 and 2.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Magento 1</span><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> is the most robust version of Magento and it is still very popular today while Magento 2 is far from comparable in popularity. Magento 1 is almost obsolete, so its use can be dangerous. But it\'s still the easiest way to get started with Magento, with a simple installation process and a well-built architecture. As a result, it will be able to support the community in the long term, even if official support ends at the end of 2018. In addition, there are many tools to transfer your code and data from Magento 1 to Magento 2 if you feel ready to upgrade your store to version 2, so there will be no problem when the time comes for Magento 2 to take over.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Magento 2</span><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> was released in 2015 and its popularity is growing rapidly, especially with the latest updates. This version has many features that speed up web development and allow customization in a more structured way than Magento 1. However, it is a much larger piece of software, so it is also more complex. Its installation requires more effort and more technical skills to understand the new development channel. However, it is important to note that the extensions are more expensive for Magento 2 than its predecessor, as its design requires additional technological knowledge.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Unlike Magento 1, Magento 2 supports many of the latest ready-made technologies, such as PHP 7, which offer significant performance improvements, image compression, improved browser caching, and the ability to use Varnish caching without a third-party extension.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 17pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Which is better? Magento 1 or Magento 2&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Magento 2 is faster, SEO friendly and more user friendly than Magento 1. Magento 2 supports the latest PHP and this improves the overall speed of the site. It may require more orders per hour and the site will load faster than Magento 1. Although Magento 2 has many performance improvements over Magento 1, you need to be proactive in optimizing the speed of your site.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 17pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Magento will always stay here</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">In all its variants, Magento is a solid e-commerce platform. Now that you know what it takes to build your online store with Magento, it\'s time to start.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000; color: #000000; font-weight: normal;"><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">You will not regret entering the world of Magento!</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="caret-color: #000000; color: #000000;"><br /><br /></span></p>', 'posts/March2022/yZE8OeXNjtQO5OJrHgTm.png', 'magento-versions-to-build-your-e-commerce-business', 'Magento Versions to build your E-Commerce Business', 'Cynosure Designs helps Businesses with supporting versions, Magento 1 and 2.', 'PENDING', 0, 0, '2022-03-15 07:58:00', '2022-03-17 06:33:28', 2),
	(12, 4, NULL, '5 digital marketing trends to be on the lookout for in 2022', 'TikTok, that has already surpassed every other social platform as the world\'s most popular social channel for Gen Z followers.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#diy">Short do-it-yourself videos</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#real_story">Tell a real story</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ai_in_digital_marketing">Artificial intelligence in digital marketing</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#quality_encounters">Quality Encounters and Conversational Marketing</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#nfts_and_crypto">NFTs and crypto in social media e-commerce</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">TikTok, which has already surpassed every other social platform as the world\'s most popular social channel for Gen Z followers. NFTs and cryptocurrencies gained traction all over the world, generating discussions about the future of finance. Google said that third-party cookies will be phased out by 2023, giving advertisers and <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">digital marketers</a> less than two years to find new ways to reach their target audiences. Most recently, Facebook changed its name to Meta to reflect the company\'s desire to embrace the metaverse, a 3D virtual environment.</p>\r\n<p>This is not it, there are a lot more advancements waiting for us to communicate and connect with each other in the digital world.</p>\r\n<p>Here are the top five digital marketing trends to watch in 2022:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="diy">Short do-it-yourself videos</h2>\r\n<p>Life is all about finding ways. As they say, &ldquo;necessity is the mother of invention&rdquo;, all of us have invented at least something in our lives. Yes you have done that! It could be anything from utilizing an empty water bottle into a flower pot or doing your makeup with your color pencils in your childhood. We have all been to something super creative. TikTok has altered the social media environment off from status updates and edited pictures and toward brief video broadcasts. Other social media platforms immediately picked up the idea and jumped on the bandwagon of reels and short videos. Instagram introduced reels after which, Facebook also followed the trend. Now short videos could have anything when it comes to content creation but research shows that DIY (do it yourself) videos are watched the most. While jumping into 2022, don&rsquo;t forget to take this idea with you. Also, you can make short reels for literally anything. If you are an engineer, teach them little engineering tasks. If you are a lazy person, you must have a bundle of DIY ideas because you know the short cuts.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="real_story">Tell a real story</h2>\r\n<p>You are thinking about <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding">brand marketing</a> and have not come up with a story yet? But wait, we are not talking about who you are and what you do. This is so mainstream and the customers are not interested in it believe me. They want to know how you delivered on your commitments in a way that met their requirements and exceeded their expectations. Stop thinking about customer reviews! It doesn\'t mean you wait for the water to reach your thirsty lips. Make a story and tell them in an impressive way. Businesses should demonstrate how their product or service may assist address a specific problem through anecdotes and client <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/casestudies">testimonials</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="ai_in_digital_marketing">Artificial intelligence in digital marketing</h2>\r\n<p>Artificial intelligence (AI) has improved a lot till now. The addition of artificial intelligence in digital marketing is a way towards more intuitive reporting, automation of common marketing activities such as site traffic monitoring, and increased search engine optimization for organic reach. But these are the things that you already know. Now is the time for us to tell you what is coming up in 2022 and onwards with a combination of digital marketing and artificial intelligence.</p>\r\n<p>AI is capable of analyzing more data at a faster rate than humans. As a result, it may use the enormous data set available to assess client purchase history and behavior. Then, you\'ll be able to recommend a certain item or deal, or even a customized advertisement.</p>\r\n<p>Using AI to predict your customer\'s next move allows you to target them with the product or service they require at the precise moment they require it. This type of targeting will result in high conversion rates and the impression that you understand your consumers\' demands without being invasive or overloading them with useless targeting.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="quality_encounters">Quality Encounters and Conversational Marketing</h2>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing">Conversational marketing</a> is nothing new for brands that have been talking with their consumers for years. Previously, field marketing was on top of everything for conversational marketing. It has still not gone out of the view. However, with the development of social media and chatbots, digital conversational marketing is becoming more prevalent and changing the landscape of how businesses connect with their consumers. This is the way towards the latest communication. Don\'t forget to leave it behind.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="nfts_and_crypto">NFTs and crypto in social media e-commerce</h2>\r\n<p>Whether you invest in cryptocurrency or not, the emergence of online currencies and NFTs has been difficult to ignore in recent years. Apparently, it might not affect your marketing strategy but that\'s not the type of passive thinking we\'re looking for in 2022!</p>\r\n<p>The idea of NFTs is to focus on the idea of selling your brand beyond the physical presence of its services and products. You can sell your brand in the air now!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>Since you know the top 5 digital marketing trends for the year, make sure you get acquainted with them and pull the maximum out of them.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/April2022/IHB38ReeTq6iXzS116Hx.jpg', '5-digital-marketing-trends-to-be-on-the-lookout-for-in-2022', 'Top digital marketing trends in 2022 | Cynosure Designs', 'TikTok, that has already surpassed every other social platform as the world\'s most popular social channel for Gen Z followers.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-04-18 04:54:00', '2022-07-26 08:58:39', 4),
	(13, 3, NULL, 'Why Does Your Business Need a Website Redesign?', 'A good website redesign is likely to increase revenue, reduce bounce rates, and improve the user experience (UX).', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#redesign_benefit">How does Website Redesign Benefit your Business?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#website_speed">When your Website Speed is Slow</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#site_responsive">To make your Site Responsive</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#outdated_design">Your Site has an Outdated Design</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#user_experience">User Experience (UX) Issues on Site</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#low_seo">Low SEO performance</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#less_conversion">Less conversion rate</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#often_need_to_redesign">How often do you need to Redesign your Website?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p id="overview">Website redesign is a detailed process that involves many changes to elements such as the code, content, structure, and visuals of your current Site to serve your visitors better. A good website redesign is likely to increase revenue, reduce bounce rates, and improve the user experience (UX). A complete website revamp includes updated content, better UI/UX, and enhanced navigation for better conversions to site performance to grow your business.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="redesign_benefit">How does Website Redesign Benefit your Business?</h2>\r\n<p>A good and attractive website redesign will help your business in the following ways:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>It enables better <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/seo">SEO</a> and gains more Organic Traffic</li>\r\n<li>Improves Site\'s Informational Flow</li>\r\n<li>Enhances Brand Image</li>\r\n<li>Increases the Leads and Conversion rates</li>\r\n<li>Boosts business Revenues</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Listed below are some reasons why your <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">website needs a Redesign</a> for your business.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="website_speed">When your Website Speed is Slow</h3>\r\n<p>Users on the Internet are generally impatient, and they don\'t like to wait for long. Research shows that almost half of modern users expect a page to load in just 2 seconds. Few people leave your Site immediately if it doesn\'t load within 3 seconds. After all, when it comes to user experience, website speed is important as slow-loading websites are never acceptable.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="site_responsive">To make your Site Responsive</h3>\r\n<p>Two significant factors show that your Site is due for a redesign.</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Not being responsive</li>\r\n<li>Not mobile-friendly</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>You must ensure that your business website provides a seamless experience on mobile devices. That doesn\'t mean it loads and looks okay on a mobile phone or tablet. Mobile-friendly websites should offer a great user experience as just your desktop website does with the same informational flow and texture. Bad performance on mobile devices can block your SEO and organic traffic.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="outdated_design">Your Site has an Outdated Design</h3>\r\n<p>The outdated design of your Site leaves a wrong impression on your business, and you are most likely to lose your customers. If your Site looks obsolete, you need to redesign your Site immediately with cutting-edge designs. Users become more discretionary about their websites, as they always want to see an attractive design in every niche.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="user_experience">User Experience (UX) Issues on Site</h3>\r\n<p>Your Site\'s <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_experience">user experience</a> must be the primary decision to give an outclass experience to customers on your website. The sites that don\'t offer a good user experience most likely have higher bounce rates, more returning visitors, and less time on pages that influence your conversion rates, search engine optimization, and brand reputation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="low_seo">Low SEO performance</h3>\r\n<p>Make sure that your website is optimized for <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Search_engine">search engines</a> because that is the only way to rank high on Google and grow your organic traffic. If your Site is not gaining organic traffic and constantly losing rankings, that is a clear sign that your Site needs a redesign. Ultimately, your Site\'s design plays a crucial role in the search engine\'s ability to crawl, index, and understand your Site. SEO is not as simple as publishing keyword-rich content, and if your SEO is not performing well, then you need to look deeper than your blog posts. 1,920 &times; 1,280</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="less_conversion">Less conversion rate</h3>\r\n<p>A low conversion rate means your Site is not serving its purpose and can result from a lack of features, complicated navigation, confusing registration forms, too many distractions, etc. Hence, there are many factors to consider and optimize your conversion rate for your website to be the next to be possible. 778 &times; 363</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="often_need_to_redesign">How often do you need to Redesign your Website?</h2>\r\n<p>The average lifespan of a website is 2 to 3 years. As design trends change and technology evolves, it is usually a time when redesign feels "fresh" and competitive. However, this time frame is only a measure, so you must identify what is best for your organization. If your Site is not working as expected, you should check to see if your Site needs a refresh or a complete redesign. Analyze and identify issues with ratings, traffic, or conversations, and then use the data to decide what to do next.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Creating Websites That Engage Users!</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/choosing-the-absolute-website-design-and-development-company-for-your-business">Choosing the Right Website Design &amp; Development Company for Your Business</a></p>', 'posts/April2022/4VVhFhr4yjFeg06EtWGA.png', 'why-does-your-business-need-a-website-redesign', 'Why Does Business Need a Website Redesign? | Cynosure Designs', 'Website Redesigning is a detailed process of updating content and layouts and improving navigation for better conversions.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-04-22 03:04:00', '2022-07-25 09:54:54', 3),
	(14, 4, NULL, 'The Top 3  UX Design Trends for 2022', 'Advancements in UX designs can help websites in gaining more user engagement. We\'ve compiled a list of the top 3 UX design trends for 2022.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#personalization">Personalization</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#AR_VR_XR">AR/VR/XR</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#data_visualization">Data Visualization</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">Knowledge &amp; technology is getting advanced so do the experiments. People discover, invent and experiment new techniques &amp; features in order to bring out the best in their <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs">UX designs</a>. These technologies &amp; features can help a user experience a smooth, advanced and attractive interaction with the website. But why did there come a need for such advancements in the first place? Advancements in UX designs can help websites in gaining more user engagement and satisfaction with the help of a smooth website experience.</p>\r\n<p>As a designer, you are required to embrace the most recent design trends in order to give clients with the finest interfaces available. But in order to adjust to the new trends, you should have a good foundation. To assist you, we\'ve compiled a list of the top 3 UX design trends for 2022. So let\'s get started:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="personalization">Personalization</h2>\r\n<p>When the control of something you love to use is in your hands, it is more attractive and convenient. Personalization has become a part of our everyday lives, with Netflix selecting programmes based on your preferences and Spotify anticipating what you want to listen to next.</p>\r\n<p>Expect a better version of such personalization in 2022. This better version of hyper-personalization will take the user experience beyond customer satisfaction. A <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">data-driven online experience</a> is expected to be delivered in which the user will get what they want even before they just ask for it. These personalizations could include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Localization for region wise login access/accounts</li>\r\n<li>Personalization of dashboards</li>\r\n<li>Personalization of notifications</li>\r\n<li>Personalization in checkout</li>\r\n<li>Personalization in website navigation/tour</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="AR_VR_XR">AR / VR / XR</h2>\r\n<p>With the advancements led by <a href="https://about.facebook.com/meta/">Meta</a> in which the company plans to create immersive digital experiences through Augmented, Virtual, and Extended Reality, (AR, VR, XR). UX design standards are bound to follow the trends. AR and VR alter the ways through which people interact with items, this increases engagement. For example, augmented reality (AR) has been employed in online store applications to allow consumers to virtually try wearing garments in their own homes. This is more likely to keep consumers interested and deliver a more seamless online experience.</p>\r\n<p>Keeping such examples in mind, UX designers must keep up with these technological advancements. They can come up with their own ideas especially when the arena of experimentation is not limited anymore.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="data_visualization">Data Visualization</h2>\r\n<p>Data visualization is not any new advancement in digital marketing, but there is a chance that it will enter a whole new realm in the year 2022. Data presentation is an important factor when displayed with simplicity. The technique of presenting data in simple, visual representations such as infographics is critical for UX designers but it can do wonders for user experience.</p>\r\n<p>Companies really would like to learn what they might do to offer data to customers in an engaging way that encourages greater interaction and increases product engagement. We can take, for example, Spotify. The yearly <a href="https://www.spotify.com/us/wrapped/">Spotify Wrapped</a> event is an excellent illustration of this.</p>\r\n<p>Showcasing customers\' favorite songs and artists, as well as their listening time, is a great approach to recognize user preferences and drive engagement. It also generates buzz on social media and serves as an excellent <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/marketing-strategy">marketing technique</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>Following these trends can do wonders in such a way that it can make a user&rsquo;s life easier by smooth digital experience which can directly affect the user&rsquo;s trust in the company. Don&rsquo;t lay back and get hit by these <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs">UX/UI advancements</a> to be one of the top user preferred websites.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Let&rsquo;s Talk Now!</a></p>', 'posts/May2022/aTlvtkXqNNhpUIgcz2NG.jpg', 'the-top-3-ux-design-trends-for-2022', 'Cynosure Designs | The Top 3  UX Design Trends for 2022', 'Advancements in UX designs can help websites in gaining more user engagement. We\'ve compiled a list of the top 3 UX design trends for 2022.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-05-19 08:50:00', '2022-07-26 08:58:08', 3),
	(15, 3, NULL, 'How are the TikTok Algorithms working in 2022?', 'TikTok’s For You Page Algorithms are a key to Gain the Competitive Advantage.', '<p>Humans continue to invent new methods to accomplish things more creatively than before, and technology advances with time. Keeping up with the changes can be very challenging for organizations.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Let&rsquo;s dive right in!</strong></p>\r\n<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#tiktok_algo">What are TikTok Algorithms, and how do they work?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#factor_foryoupage">What factors does &ldquo;For You Page&rdquo; content considers?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#factor_foryoupage_doesnt">What factors &ldquo;For You, Page&rdquo; content Does Not consider?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#factors_choosing">How to work with the TikTok Algorithms in 2022?</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#switch_to_pro">Switch to Pro Account</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#high_quality_content">Create High-Quality Content</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#write_caption">Write a Caption that creates Curiosity</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#engage_audience">Post at the Right Time to Engage the Audience</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#analytics_account">See the Analytics of your content</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#trending_music">Use Trending Music in your videos</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#find_sounds">How do you determine which music and sounds are popular? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#add_hashtags">Don&rsquo;t forget to add the right HashTags in your content</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#hastag_foryou">Hashtags for the For You page</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#trending_hashtags">Trending HashTags</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>With technological advancements, <strong>Cynosure Designs</strong> have identified the new significant trends of TitTok Algorithms that will be important to propel towards a better future. In <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">Social Media Marketing</a>, the TikTok platform is vital in promoting your brand awareness and gaining the customer&rsquo;s engagement.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Companies need to know about the TikTok algorithm in 2022 and beyond.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="tiktok_algo">What are TikTok Algorithms, and how do they work?</h2>\r\n<p>&ldquo;The TikTok algorithm is a suggestion system that selects which <a href="https://newsroom.tiktok.com/en-us/how-tiktok-recommends-videos-for-you">videos to display</a> on your For You Page.&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On the For You page, no two users will watch the identical videos, and the videos you see may change over time based on your viewing choices and even your present state of mind. The stream of videos is tailored to your preferences, making it simple to discover material and creators you enjoy driven by the recommendation engine. The app\'s addictiveness originates from the highly tailored TikTok algorithm that powers your For You feed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="factor_foryoupage">&ldquo;For You Page&rdquo; content is based on the following factors:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The videos you watch to the end</li>\r\n<li>accounts you follow</li>\r\n<li>Videos you like</li>\r\n<li>The content you share</li>\r\n<li>Comments you post</li>\r\n<li>The content you create on your account</li>\r\n<li>The interest you show in your interaction</li>\r\n<li>The marked videos as not interested</li>\r\n<li>Country preference (you may be more likely to see the content from people in your own country)</li>\r\n<li>Categories of interest that you select</li>\r\n<li>Language preference</li>\r\n<li>Trending topics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="factor_foryoupage_doesnt">TikTok Algorithms do Not consider the following types of content for the &ldquo;For You Page&rdquo;:</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The content you have already seen</li>\r\n<li>Duplicated content</li>\r\n<li>Spam content</li>\r\n<li>Upsetting content</li>\r\n<li>Followers count</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="factors_choosing">How to work with the TikTok Algorithms in 2022?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="switch_to_pro">1-Switch to Pro Account</h3>\r\n<p><a href="https://www.tiktok.com">TikTok</a> has two types of pro accounts based on whether you are a creator or a business. Although having a pro account will not help you get your videos on the For You page, switching to one is a crucial aspect of knowing the TikTok algorithm. This is because a Creator or Business account offers you access to analytics and insights that may help guide your TikTok strategy. Understanding who your audience is, when they are active on the app, and what kind of content they prefer is important if you want to develop content that they will enjoy and engage with.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>To switch to a TikTok Business account, follow these steps:&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tap the three dots symbol at the upper right of the screen from your profile page.</li>\r\n<li>Select Manage Account.</li>\r\n<li>Select Switch to Business Account and then select the appropriate category for your business.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/June2022/tiktok-on-mobile.webp" alt="TikTok on Mobile" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="high_quality_content">2- Create High-Quality Content</h3>\r\n<p>Low-quality content will not get a way to the For You page. You don\'t need expensive equipment; your phone is the ideal instrument for producing realistic videos. You\'ll need good lighting, a strong microphone, and some rapid edits to keep the content going. TikTok may last from 5 seconds to 3 minutes but aim for 12-15 seconds to keep your viewers captivated. You must shoot in the 9:16 vertical format. Vertically filmed videos have a 25% greater six-second watch-through rate. Create your videos with the trending sound; according to 88 per cent of users, music is "important" on TikTok.</p>\r\n<p>Moreover, View-through rates are higher for fast-paced tunes that play at 120 beats per minute. Also, take advantage of TikTok\'s built-in features, including effects and text modifications. For the greatest algorithm TikTok impact, try experimenting with trending effects.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="write_caption">3- Write a Caption that creates Curiosity for TikTok</h3>\r\n<p>Use your caption to stimulate people\'s interest and engagement or ask a question that will generate a discussion in the comments. TikTok captions are limited to 150 characters, including hashtags. But that\'s not a reason to ignore this valuable feature. A good caption reminds viewers why they should watch your video, boosting the algorithm\'s engagement and video completion rating signals. Captions are an excellent method to reach a wider audience with your TikTok videos. They improve the general accessibility of a video, allowing more viewers to appreciate your content. Whether you use TikTok\'s auto-captions or add your own, both methods will bring something special to your videos.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="engage_audience">4- Post at the Right Time to Engage the Audience</h3>\r\n<p>Posting the right content at the right time is important for all social media platforms. The same applies to TikTok, where the algorithms consider active involvement with your content. TikTok suggests publishing 1-4 times each day. Because every audience is unique, check your Business or Creator account metrics to see when your audience is most engaged.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read More:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/how-to-reach-the-right-audience-with-digital-marketing">How to Reach the Right Audience with Digital Marketing</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="analytics_account">To see the analytics of your content:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tap the three dots symbol at the upper right of the screen from your profile page.</li>\r\n<li>Select Business Suite</li>\r\n<li>Tap Analytics.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="trending_music">5- Use Trending Music in your videos</h3>\r\n<p>How important is music on TikTok? The research showed that 88% of TikTok users said sound is essential for the TikTok experience as the sound-on approach makes the content special and engaging for the users. TikToker prefers brand videos that feature popular or trending tunes, as following any trend is a smart bet when aiming for the For You page. TikTok Analytics may help you determine which sounds are popular with your target demographic.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="find_sounds">So, how do you determine which music and sounds are popular?&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tap the plus symbol at the bottom of the TikTok home screen</li>\r\n<li>Tap Sounds on the Record Video page.</li>\r\n<li>You\'ll find a list of the most popular sounds.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="add_hashtags">6- Don&rsquo;t forget to add the right HashTags in your content</h3>\r\n<p>Adding a certain hashtag to a video will make the content more discoverable when someone searches for the hashtag. There are two kinds of hashtags that can help your content rank higher in the TikTok algorithm:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li id="hastag_foryou"><strong>Hashtags for the For You page:</strong> Tags such as <strong>#fyp</strong>, <strong>#foryou</strong>, and <strong>#foryoupage</strong> are frequently used in an attempt to get onto the For You page. TikTok would not confirm whether they work, but considering the number of accounts that use them, it\'s worth a shot, as Chipotle does in this post.</li>\r\n<li id="trending_hashtags"><strong>Trending HashTags:</strong> Go to the Discover tab, then hit Trends at the top of the page to see popular hashtags. Keep an eye out for hashtags relating to challenges, as they are a great method to generate creative content ideas while also sending positive trend vibes to the algorithm.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>TikTok&rsquo;s For You Page Algorithms are a key to gain the Competitive Advantage. Look no further and <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">contact our experts</a> for our most specialized Digital Marketing Services.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/5-digital-marketing-trends-to-be-on-the-lookout-for-in-2022">5 Digital Marketing Trends To Be On The Lookout For In 2022</a></p>', 'posts/June2022/bvacP5FAWoyRFWwpSZyi.webp', 'how-are-the-tiktok-algorithms-working-in-2022', 'How are the TikTok Algorithms working in 2022?', 'The TikTok algorithm is a suggestion system that selects which videos to display on your For You Page', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-06-09 04:00:00', '2022-06-26 17:00:17', 5),
	(16, 4, NULL, 'Six Types of Branding Services', 'The personality of your brand doesn\'t solely depend on logos, name, and colors but it depends on everything that makes it a brand.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#importance_of_branding">Importance of Branding </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#branding_services">What are branding services? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#why_are_service_imp">Why are branding services important? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#types_of_branding">What are the types of branding services? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#stages_of_branding">Stages of branding? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#branding_for_small_bs">Branding services for small businesses? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final thought. </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">You might have heard about branding services and how helpful they could be if not then, let us tell you that a company with the help of branding services can sail through literally any struggle that it might be going through. It could be from creating a brand identity from zero to getting recognized by a vast level of audience across the globe. In this article we will discuss:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="importance_of_branding">What is branding &amp; its importance?</h2>\r\n<p>The word <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding" target="_blank" rel="noopener">branding</a> itself is pretty clear in defining it. It means naming something or promoting it. It won&rsquo;t be wrong to announce that yes we exist. Just the way a baby is born and he is named and announcements are made that we have got a little angel at our home, likewise, your business needs the same attention from a unique beautiful name to its existence and presence to get the attention of people to whom it might be of interest.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/6-thing-about-branding1.webp" alt="mini sites" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The personality of your brand doesn\'t solely depend on logos, name, and colors but it depends on everything that makes it a brand. Promotion or branding of a business has always been in place for centuries but now it has become a necessity for a business to make its foundations stand in the market of uncountable competitors.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="branding_services">What are branding services?</h2>\r\n<p>So, now we have talked about the importance of branding services already but what exactly are the branding services? This includes everything from the name of the business, its logo, how it is communicated and promoted to the public, etc. So, all of these things are done with the help of branding services. Some companies offer <strong>branding services in the UK for</strong> promoting your business in a better way. These services might include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Designing of a Logo</li>\r\n<li>Your Brand Slogan</li>\r\n<li>Positioning of the brand</li>\r\n<li>Your brand voice</li>\r\n<li>Styling of the brand</li>\r\n<li>Social media branding</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/6-thing-about-branding2.webp" alt="one page websites" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Also read: </strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/logo-defines-your-brand" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Logo Defines Your Brand</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="why_are_service_imp">Why are branding services important?</h2>\r\n<p>Branding is important because no one would ever know that you exist if you would not tell them. We all use social media and see so many brands coming across our social feed. Even if we buy something from a brand, we might forget it later on because of so many of the other suggestions and options. So, imagine if you are not there on social media or you don&rsquo;t have your online presence and you are not promoting your business, how would a customer even look at your business in a world where they have other options in abundance? So, yes it has become amazing for a layman to buy from multiple options but you as a business need only one thing to be focused on the most and that is branding.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/6-thing-about-branding3.webp" alt="mini sites" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="types_of_branding">What are the types of branding services?</h2>\r\n<p>Depending on the nature of your business, the <strong>branding services</strong> could be as per your need. For example, if you are a company that offers services rather than products, the branding services would be provided accordingly. On the other hand, if you are a company that produces products, your branding server will help your products reach your potential customers via product branding. There are different types of branding services as per the need of a brand niche which include:</p>\r\n<h3>1- Product branding.</h3>\r\n<p>In every branding strategy product branding is at the top particularly when you are a product seller. When the branding strategy principles are applied to a particular product for its promotion, that is called product branding. These principles might include giving a symbol to the product, naming it, and creating a unique design of it to have a unique identity. For example if you are a company named ABC, and you produce a product called a spatula, now you have recently planned to produce another product called a hammer.</p>\r\n<p>Your customers might know you as a brand ABC that sells spatulas but in order to have a new unique identity of your new product hammer, you must come up with a whole new product branding making the product stand like your previous product. To make you understand in easier terms, a producer of a movie could be one person whereas, he or she can produce a 100 movies under his production team. Every movie has a unique name, story and promotional campaigns. No one recognizes the new movie with the name of the previous one. Each one has its own identity. Likewise, product branding is also somewhat like that.</p>\r\n<h3>2- Service branding.</h3>\r\n<p>It is no different than the product branding as the services of a provider becomes its products and then everything goes the same way as of the product branding. The idea is the same as the previous one to have a unique identity, name and recognition of the service that you are offering. Although the two are the same , service branding is a bit complex as compared to product branding. In service branding, you might need front line staff, providers of the service, employees maintaining the service and all other stakeholders associated with it.</p>\r\n<p>For example, if you have created an application that helps the customers find their nearest locations with respect to food, this is a service come product. You might need both product and service branding as your application might need all the special treatment that a product might need. On the other hand, you might need to keep updating your application, keep informing the customers and teaching them on how to use it and keep in contact with them via customer service.</p>\r\n<h3>3- Retail branding.</h3>\r\n<p>Retail branding is another form of branding which includes a shop name on the whole. For example, you might know many superstores that sell all types of products. Now these products become a part of the brand itself and retail branding includes the promotion of that specific store. This might include building customer loyalty and building long term customer relationships with the store brand.</p>\r\n<p>Loyalty refers to a continuous process in which the customers repeatedly buy products of that brand. Once your customers start identifying your store products, the gap between you and the customers has already been filled. That&rsquo;s the main purpose of retail branding to make your customers recognize you out of the crowd.</p>\r\n<h3>4- Online branding.</h3>\r\n<p>It is the era of the internet,everything has been shifted to online platforms. You can build your identity or your brand&rsquo;s identity on internet with the help of different platforms such as by making a website, registering yourself on Google, making your social media accounts onInstagram, Facebook, YouTube etc. with the help of online branding, you can introduce yourself online with a vast group of audience.</p>\r\n<p>Optimizing your online presence is the most effective strategy to boost lead generation, conversion, and brand sales if you manage a business, an e-commerce site, or own a brand. Improving brand exposure, recognition, and reputation also requires building a brand online.</p>\r\n<h3>5- Corporate branding.</h3>\r\n<p>The word corporate itself tells you that this branding includes the promotion on corporate levels. Every aspect of a professional corporation is covered under corporate branding. If you have a company, you might need to present yourself to the world. Corporate branding is exactly the way you do that. You as a start up corporation might need to first focus on various things such as your business niche, your direction, your target market etc. the second thing is to identify who are you company&rsquo;s stakeholders as they all play an important role in defining who you are to the world.</p>\r\n<p>Every successful business has a logo, a tagline, or other visual representation of its goods or services. These could take the shape of vows, customs, or identities. Think of a brand that is famous and almost everyone knows about it. Let&rsquo;s take for example, Google, how do we know that it exists and what does it do? We know it as a company, not as what it does in particular. Likewise, corporate branding is about a branding strategy on the whole.</p>\r\n<h3>6- Offline branding.</h3>\r\n<p>Offline branding might sound like an old idea but it is still very important to brands and companies in order to sell what they offer or produce. Offline marketing includes everything that is not digital for example, billboards, field marketing campaigns, banners, pamphlets etc. Such as when you go to shop for something and in the end you get a pamphlet by a salesperson, that is exactly offline branding. They are letting you know that we exist physically.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/6-thing-about-branding4.webp" alt="branding 4" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="stages_of_branding">Stages of branding?</h2>\r\n<p>Everything starts with research and ends with a conclusion and outcome. When you want to start a company, you look at all of the aspects including your budget, the product or service you wish to launch, and its demand in the market. You take a start only after that. Likewise, in branding services, some stages need to be followed to have the right <strong>branding</strong> process for your business. These stages include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Research</li>\r\n<li>Strategy</li>\r\n<li>Designing</li>\r\n<li>Implementation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="branding_for_small_bs">Branding services for small businesses?</h2>\r\n<p>Most people think that it is important for large-scale businesses to have branding services and pre-planning, but this is the wrong narrative. For small businesses, branding services are extremely important and they can easily acquire these services as the business is small and it will take half the time and assets as compared to large-scale business. Branding services for small businesses can be extremely useful as small businesses need more attention and strong foundations with low investments. So, making a small investment and letting it drown is an unskilled thing in itself. There should be zero chances for small businesses to fail but it is only possible with the help of a clear <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/marketing-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketing strategy</a> , strong vision, and <strong>best branding services.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>Branding services are important for all types of businesses because, in a world of <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">digital marketing</a> and a lot of branding and promoting options, a business cannot survive and live its potential life without opting for these ways. Another thing companies don&rsquo;t understand is where to go and which company to hire for branding services. So, if you are looking for a <strong>branding services company</strong> inside or outside of the UK, <strong>Cynosure Designs</strong> offers everything under one roof for your business to grow digitally.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>People Also Read: </strong><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/what-can-a-digital-marketing-company-do-for-your-business-in-two-steps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">What Can A Digital Marketing Company Do For Your Business In Two Steps?</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/July2022/5QYKcgl3avUArJ723xeg.webp', 'six-types-of-branding-services', 'Six Types of Branding Services | Cynosure Designs', 'A company with the help of branding services can sail through literally any struggle that it might be going through.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 1, '2022-07-28 12:57:00', '2022-08-05 10:32:50', 7),
	(17, 4, NULL, 'What are the 7 Types of Digital Marketing?', 'Digital marketing has become an integral component of an organisation\'s overall marketing strategy.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#diff_types_of_dm">Different Types of Digital Marketing </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#seo">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ppc">Pay-per-Click (PPC) </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#social_media_marketing">Social Media Marketing </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#content_marketing">Content Marketing </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#email_marketing">Email Marketing </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#mobile_marketing">Mobile Marketing </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#marketing_analytics">Marketing Analytics </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">Over the last decade, digital marketing has become an integral component of an organisation\'s overall marketing strategy. Businesses may tailor their messages to a specific target, allowing them to market directly to individuals who are likely to be interested in their product. Digital marketing encompasses a broad variety of marketing methods and technologies used to reach clients online.</p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="diff_types_of_dm">Different Types of Digital Marketing</h2>\r\n<p>This post will teach you 7 top digital marketing methods to help your company develop internationally.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/1-seo.webp" alt="seo" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="seo">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h2>\r\n<p>The goal of SEO is for a company\'s website to rank higher in Google search results, resulting in more visits. To do this, SEO marketers research the keywords and phrases that people use while searching for information online and include those terms into their own content.</p>\r\n<p>So, what are some of the factors that may aid a site\'s SEO? One of the elements that makes SEO challenging is that the answer is always dependent on Google and its most recent algorithm. With this in mind, here are a few of the most important things SEO strategists and marketers in general should understand about how <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/seo">SEO</a> works today.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Content indexing - It is vital to provide alt text for images and text transcripts for video and audio material to allow search engines to correctly "understand" your site content.</li>\r\n<li>Good link structure &mdash; Search engines must be able to "crawl" your site structure and swiftly discover all of your material. An SEO specialist may do a variety of things to appropriately organise links, URLs, and sitemaps so that site crawlers can readily access them.</li>\r\n<li>Keywords and targeted keywords - One of the most important SEO building blocks is correctly deploying your keywords &ndash; i.e. the search terms you want your site to be discovered for &ndash; in your content and headers. It is no longer advisable to "stuff" your content with as many keywords and keyword variations as possible. Writing high-quality content with keywords in headers and a few times in crawlable page content is now considered best practice, and it will help pages rank better in search results.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/2-ppc.webp" alt="ppc" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="ppc">Pay-per-Click (PPC)</h2>\r\n<p>Sponsored search engine results and banner ads are examples of pay-per-click advertising. This is a sort of short-term digital marketing in which the ad will disappear if you stop paying. PPC is a method of increasing a company\'s internet search traffic, similar to SEO.</p>\r\n<p>Commercials that show at the top and sides of search results pages, advertisements that appear when surfing the web, advertisements that run before YouTube movies, and advertisements that appear in mobile applications are all examples of pay-per-click advertising.</p>\r\n<p>Another difference between <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/seo">PPC</a> and SEO is that you just pay for the results. You will only be compensated when someone clicks on your ad and visits your website in a traditional PPC technique, such as a Google AdWords campaign. You may spend nearly any amount of money on pay-per-click advertising. Many big organisations spend tens of thousands of dollars each month on pay-per-click advertising, while other businesses may see results after paying only a few hundred dollars.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/3-social-media-marketing.webp" alt="social media marketing" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="social_media_marketing">Social Media Marketing</h2>\r\n<p>This includes everything a business does on social media channels. Despite the fact that practically everyone is familiar with social media, marketers must use it in a coordinated and strategic manner. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">Social media marketing</a> entails a lot more than just publishing to social media sites and responding to comments.</p>\r\n<p>To be effective, efforts must be coordinated and consistent, rather than being a mistake. There are a plethora of online tools for scheduling and organising social media posts to help keep messaging consistent, but marketers should treat digitalization as a tool rather than a "set it and forget it" solution. If there is no real person behind the posts, users will notice right away.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Also read:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/how-are-the-tiktok-algorithms-working-in-2022">How Are The TikTok Algorithms Working In 2022?</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/4-content-marketing.webp" alt="content marketing" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="content_marketing">Content Marketing</h2>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing">Content marketing</a> uses story and information sharing to increase brand identification. The ultimate goal is for the reader to take a step toward becoming a customer, such as requesting more information, signing up for an email list, or making a purchase. Blog postings, resources such as journal articles and e-books, digital video, webcasts, and a number of other things are all examples of "content." In general, rather than merely advertising the brand or seeking to sell something, it should first and foremost provide value to the consumer. Rather than completing a single sale, content marketing focuses on building a long-term, trusted relationship with your customers that may lead to several transactions over time.</p>\r\n<p>Material marketing is a means of inserting SEO search terms into new website material, and the content created may be distributed as online articles and email marketing publications, as well as other kinds of digital marketing. Analysing your content marketing data may tell a lot about your customers, such as what they\'re looking for when they come to your website. What kinds of information entices people to remain longer on the site and look around? What sorts of things catch their interest and make them want to leave?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/5-email-marketing.webp" alt="email marketing" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="email_marketing">Email Marketing</h2>\r\n<p>Despite the development of social media, smartphone apps, and other channels, Rogers claims that email is still one of the most effective marketing methods. It might be utilised as part of a content marketing strategy to deliver advantages to existing consumers while also converting new ones.</p>\r\n<p>The accessible rate &ndash; the percentage of recipients who launched the email &ndash; and the ctr &ndash; the number of recipients who opened the email and clicked on a link inside the email &ndash; are two analytics metrics recommended in email marketing software that marketers are continuously attempting to improve. There are various things advertisers can do to make their emails more appealing to customers and more likely to be read, according to Constant Contact, a prominent <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing">email marketing </a> software company.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/6-mobile-marketing.webp" alt="mobile marketing" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="mobile_marketing">Mobile Marketing</h2>\r\n<p>The goal of this type of digital marketing is to reach out to your target demographic via their smartphone or tablet. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing"> Mobile marketing</a> reaches people through text messaging, social media, internet, email, and mobile apps. Marketers can tailor special offers or information to a certain location or time, such as when a client enters a store or attends an event.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/7-marketing-analytics.webp" alt="marketing analytics" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="marketing_analytics">Marketing Analytics</h2>\r\n<p>The fact that web <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/marketing-strategy">marketing</a> is so measurable and quantitative is one of its most major advantages. Once upon a time, offers and similar direct mail offers were the only trackable marketing goods. If a customer took advantage of the offer, you knew the message had been received. Marketers can now track user behaviour in great detail, such as how many times they click on a link, how long they remain on a web page, how often they read emails, and so on, thanks to analytics. On the other hand, the massive amount of data available on digital marketing performance might feel like drinking from a fire hose, and marketers must be able to properly comprehend what the data means and how it should guide strategy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Get all of these services with <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">Cynosure Designs.</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/July2022/JkEEjWAUuhYibJo3O1ZE.webp', 'what-are-the-7-types-of-digital-marketing', 'Cynosure UK | 7 Types of Digital Marketing?', 'Digital marketing is an integral component of a company’s marketing strategy. 7 top digital marketing methods to help your company develop internationally', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-07-29 08:59:00', '2022-07-29 09:21:39', 5),
	(18, 4, NULL, 'Everything about lead generation in digital marketing', 'A lead is defined as someone who expresses a desire to participate in a brand or business in any manner.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#types_of_leads">Types of leads </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_is_lead_gen">What is lead generation? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_use_of_lead">What is the use of lead generation? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ways_to_gen">Ways to generate leads </a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#demos">Demos</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#contests">Contests</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#email_sub">Email Subscriptions </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#free_apps">Free Apps </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">A lead is defined as someone who expresses a desire to participate in a brand or business in any manner. A marketing lead is a user that expresses a desire in a brand\'s merchandise, so becoming a prospective customer. Just about every company\'s principal purpose is to create quite so many leads that are feasible. A firm should mentor customers through the sales pipeline by providing them with appropriate material and promotions that will lead to a buying.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/1-types-of-leads.webp" alt="types of leads" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="types_of_leads">Types of leads</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Information qualified lead </strong>These prospects are at the start of the customer lifecycle. At this point, a corporation must provide useful knowledge on the topic related to the user\'s inquiry in return for private details such as their identity, email address, region, and so forth.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sales qualified lead </strong>people who come and show interest in a product or service. This is also referred to as a hot lead.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Marketing qualified lead </strong>Such leads will be in the midst of the selling process. Individuals who have shown or are willing to show continued interest in a business. This is sometimes referred to as a "warm lead."</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id="what_is_lead_gen">What is lead generation?</h2>\r\n<p>Lead generation is the process of drawing consumers to a company and developing their attention via support, with the ultimate objective of turning people into customers. Job applications, blog articles, discounts, live events, and online material are all ways to create <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding">leads</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/2-what-is-lead-generation.webp" alt="what is lead generation" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="what_use_of_lead">What is the use of lead generation?</h2>\r\n<p>Lead generation helps a business find its potential buyers of its services and products by applying various methods digitally. A process where the information of customers is held and they are guided and informed about the company and its products based on their interests. Lead generation helps in increasing the interest of people in a company to a point where they become the buyers. It helps in increasing the sales in every perspective. It can help businesses of any type whether they are smaller or larger enterprises. A lack of lead generation strategy could result in waiting for a lifetime for the real <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/marketing-strategy">potential customers </a> for a company.</p>\r\n<p>It is not limited to this but it also helps in increasing the visibility, credibility, trust, and interest of a certain set of individuals to certain sets of products or services. With the right lead generation tactics, you can expand your business and increase the lifespan customer acquisition cost.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/2-One-page-websites.webp" alt="one page website" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="ways_to_gen">Ways to generate leads</h2>\r\n<h3 id="demos">Demos</h3>\r\n<p>Make it simple for users who want to know further about your item or brand to book a demonstration with your company. Demonstration demands may be put on critical sections of the website, such as the main website page.</p>\r\n<p>All of those are especially useful in areas of a website that discuss the many qualities and characteristics of any good or service. Once the customer is interested, consider scheduling a demonstration as simple as possible.</p>\r\n<h3 id="contests">Contests</h3>\r\n<p>Consumers enjoy challenges. They may educate you much about your market audience by engaging consumers, expanding brand\'s reach, increasing traffic to websites, and generating leads. Contests may be held on a webpage or on virtually any social networking site, such as Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, and Instagram. They may be as basic or as complex as you want to:</p>\r\n<h3 id="email_sub">Email Subscriptions</h3>\r\n<p>Enterprise blog posting not just increases visitors to a website, but it may also really be a significant reason for the increased lead creation in the future. But turning traffic into reading a blog could be rocket science.</p>\r\n<p>First, convert visitors into loyal subscribers by persuading them for their email address in return for daily, weekly, or monthly blog entries. Include a one-step registration on your blog to make it simple for people to subscribe.</p>\r\n<h3 id="free_apps">Free Apps</h3>\r\n<p>Who has said a free product can\'t generate business? They are, in fact, a fantastic potential for lead generation. Try offering free versions of your product or service &ndash; they can be compact or have less characteristics than the full-fledged version with no risk, commitment, or bank card involved. Just one thing they have to do is complete a form.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Want to apply all of these ways to your website to generate leads? <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Try us today!</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/July2022/F5jAFseCFDCjKuF9fOje.webp', 'everything-about-lead-generation-in-digital-marketing', 'Cynosure Designs | lead generation in digital marketing', 'A marketing lead is a user that expresses a desire in a brand\'s merchandise. Lead generation helps a business find its potential buyers.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-07-29 09:40:00', '2022-07-29 10:29:27', 5),
	(19, 4, NULL, 'AI in Analytics helps in deep customer insights', 'The magic of artificial intelligence will help you catch the deep insights of people who might be looking for something that you are selling.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#are_you_listening">Are you listening to your customers? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#magic_behind">The Magic of AI Behind Reading Minds </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#purpose_of_con">What&rsquo;s the purpose of consumer insights? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#how_can_you">How can you as a company track your customer behavior? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">You might have heard &ldquo;think of a yellow car and you will come across a yellow car in abundance&rdquo;. That&rsquo;s what a the <a href="https://www.verywellmind.com/understanding-and-using-the-law-of-attraction-3144808#:~:text=The%20law%20of%20attraction%20is,negative%20thoughts%20bring%20negative%20outcomes.">law of attraction</a> is but when you think of a yellow car and it appears in your social media feed, or on any website you are scrolling. What is that? Nature calls it the law of attraction, we call it artificial intelligence. So, do you have your yellow car and want it to be seen by the people thinking of it? Let us pull out the magic sticks and catch the minds. So, are you ready for the magical ride? Let&rsquo;s go then!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="are_you_listening">Are you listening to your customers?</h2>\r\n<p>Some people believe that social media apps or even switching on the internet will have them get listened to secretly. But that is not the case, as the big names running these platforms themselves raised questions like us that is technology listening to us. <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/tech/facebook-listening-listen-does-is-microphone-app-phone-mark-zuckerberg-a8299281.html">Mark Zuckerberg called it a conspiracy</a> in an interview when he was asked the same question.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/July2022/1-listen-to-customers.webp" alt="listen to customers" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We are back to real life again but wait, the magic is still here. The magic of artificial intelligence will help you catch the deep insights of people who might be looking for something that you are selling. How interesting it is, isn\'t it? But how do we do it? So if nobody is listening to us, what&rsquo;s the real story behind it?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="magic_behind">The Magic of AI Behind Reading Minds</h2>\r\n<p>Yes! It is the sorcery of Artificial Intelligence. It is not less than a modern logical wizard. Do you remember the magic shows in schools where the wizard would make us fool by his sharp mind and a few tricks of actions and observations and we would believe it as a paranormal activity? Likewise, artificial intelligence is all about recording your actions online and offline. We immediately or on the same day, see those things in our feed that we thought about or talked about because technology tracks us. It tracks what we click, what we search in abundance, which posts we stop at the most, which website we open the most, which colors we look at the most, and which ads we consider the most. All of this behavior is tracked and it is more like a technically psychological tracking that predicts what we might think of next.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/July2022/2-aI-behind-reading-minds.webp" alt="AI behind reading minds" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Imagine you have been living with a roommate in a hostel for the past five years. You would know your roommate&rsquo;s routine more than anyone. If someone comes at 4 pm and inquires about your roommate, whether you have seen him going somewhere or not, you will make a guess and say, he might be at the gym right now. This is because you have been observing his actions naturally. So, now imagine the numbers game is so strong. There is no chance for it to take a wrong stride. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing">Artificial intelligence</a> keeps on recording your routine interaction with the websites, social media platforms, videos, etc, and suggests you accordingly. Also, if you talked about something with your friend that you didn&rsquo;t search for, it is you who forgot but AI kept it recorded when you randomly stopped at a post relevant to what you talked about with your friend. No matter if you clicked the like button or not your insight was delivered as a potential consumer to any brand or company through consumer analytics.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="purpose_of_con">What&rsquo;s the purpose of consumer insights?</h2>\r\n<p>Now as you have enough knowledge about the consumer insights and how they are tracked, the question here is what are they useful for? What will technology do with it if I see an ad that I thought about? Well, this is what the technology will do if it gets successful in showing you what you were thinking about.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Makes you reach out to the right websites and platforms that you might need for buying something.</li>\r\n<li>Helps you get seen by the people who might be interested in buying something from your business.</li>\r\n<li>It might help you get deep insights as a business about the visitors and customers on your website.</li>\r\n<li>You as a business can utilize the information gathered through deep customer insights in determining the pace of your business.</li>\r\n<li>You can make products as per the need of the customers without asking your customers through the engagement of the visitors on your website or social portal such that which products were liked the most and which products were ignored</li>\r\n<li>These analytics can help you produce only those things which have high demand and help you save a lot of money.</li>\r\n<li>You can assess which services and products are liked the most region-wise and can customize every product and service as per the demand region wise</li>\r\n<li>You might also maintain your website by looking into the analytics such that which web page has scrolled up the most and can make the rest of the pages as smooth as that page.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/July2022/3-consumer-insights.webp" alt="consumer insights" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Also read: <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/the-top-3-ux-design-trends-for-2022"> The top 3 UX designs trends for 2022</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="how_can_you">How can you as a company track your customer behavior?</h2>\r\n<p>When a formula is made, we don&rsquo;t need the formula maker to keep making thousands of samples every time but we simply buy the formula and make the product ourselves. That is how you do it. Tracking your customer behavior through AI analytics is possible with the help of an expert who bought the formula of AI analytics through learning it.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>The right digital marketing company can help you in assessing your website and telling you what is missing and how you can fix it. Using artificial intelligence, a digital marketing company can help you look deep down into your website&rsquo;s visitors&rsquo; behavior and can turn them into your potential customers. They can do it using social media marketing, pay-per-click, content marketing, website redesign, and search engine optimization with a whole website audit. So, what makes you wait to think about making a maximum profit out of your business? Maybe a link to contact the right place!</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Contact us now!</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>People also search for: <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/how-to-reach-the-right-audience-with-digital-marketing">how to reach the right audience with digital marketing?</a></strong></p>', 'posts/July2022/6DX3eT2evXgaaKiVYe22.webp', 'ai-in-analytics-helps-in-deep-customer-insights', 'Cynosure | AI in Analytics helps in deep customer insights', 'Artificial intelligence is all about recording your actions online and offline. Get deep customer insights using social media marketing, pay-per-click, content marketing.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-07-29 10:05:23', '2022-07-29 10:05:23', 7),
	(20, 4, NULL, 'Website Redesign 2022: Boost Traffic And Sales With These Redesigning Tips', 'Web designing is a technical art and designers are expanding their ways to show off their creativity.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#delightful">Delightful Mini-sites </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#one_page">One-page websites. </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#web_based">Web-based scavenger hunts/web activity </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">Web designers have taken a shift in the work and have started creating sites as art. Art? Yes, you read it right. Web designing is a technical art and designers are expanding their ways to show off their creativity. This is what is selling in the market as well because it is something that maybe you too would want to see. It started back when the designers played with techniques to create websites for themselves and when it comes to your own thing, your area of experiment is infinite.</p>\r\n<p>Remember when the web was emerging and we would just enjoy the basic and simple things? Among all, my favorite was <strong>Google Dinosaur Game! </strong> It won&rsquo;t be wrong to say that we have landed in the earlier web period just like renaissance. As everything is shifting to 90s ideas and creativity then why not web designs. Well, obviously this fusion of high technology and that old creativity is nonetheless the best one yet.</p>\r\n<p>Taking the past creativity and future techniques, web design is evolving. This movement into the future is exciting and techniques like advanced interactions and animations and visual effects like <a href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/glassmorphism-design-effect-with-html-css/">glassmorphism</a> and grain. No code tools are used by designers to make it even smoother and easier.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="delightful">Delightful Mini-sites</h2>\r\n<p>The world is in a scarcity of happiness and people rarely get attracted towards anything nowadays. As they say, excess of everything is bad, this is what has happened to us. Having an excess of technology, designs, tools and everything in our access has made us immune to everything. We don&rsquo;t get excited over things anymore. So, putting some humor into your web design can definitely get you some happy customers. Imagine a website that provokes laughter?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/1-mini-sites.webp" alt="mini sites" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>But what is a <a href="https://www.absoluteweb.com/what-is-a-minisite/">minisite</a> ? Well, as the name suggests, it is the smaller version of your website. You may say, it can be used for targeting a particular purpose without expanding it to all in one site. You can create special attractive graphics, animations and attract customers to a particular product or service without letting them stray into a bundle of things right in front of them.</p>\r\n<p>Now let&rsquo;s get back to humor. You can add humor to the site navigation, images, animation, videos and even content. A happy mind can become a happy customer and what else would you want? Imagine people coming to your website to enjoy the navigation humor? As they say fake it until you make it, we would say make it look like a serious site until they explore it is not!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="one_page">One-page websites.</h2>\r\n<p>In a busy life having no time, who would spend time on a complex website? Especially when they have a bundle of options to jump to. Many times, it turns out that the least complex site is the most effective one. These one page websites are based on one <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs">HTML page.</a> Single-page websites are ideal for those who want to attract a certain niche and give them a specific sort of user experience. Particularly when you don\'t have to be worried about people clicking on multiple pages, potentially in the wrong order, it\'s easy to regulate their behavior on your site and lead them in a certain way.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/2-One-page-websites.webp" alt="one page websites" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>These websites give the impression of carrying a leaflet or reading a poster. Every single information that you might need to search can be found on one page and one place without looking for multiple pages.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="web_based">Web-based scavenger hunts/web activity</h2>\r\n<p>Human beings run behind curiosity and when there is none and you disclose everything, it&rsquo;s all boring again. So, keep a few things hidden and make them enjoy reaching the truth. Well, it is not a suspense movie, but yes the architecture of websites really lend themselves quite well to riddles and scavenger hunts. You can make different puzzles on the website, or put on some games or questions for the user to unlock the next step or information. Oh, we talked about a suspense movie so, yes make it a suspense website and make them stick to it till the end.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/posts/July2022/1-mini-sites.webp" alt="mini sites" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There are several inventive methods for concealing and revealing prompts, hints, and solutions. This is an example of how you can utilize your web design skills to create an enthralling puzzle.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Display a word and let them solve it by riddle/clue</li>\r\n<li>Make them hunt, hide a word and let them find in your website</li>\r\n<li>Put a game on your website</li>\r\n<li>Let them be creative, make them draw shapes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>This is not it, there are a hundred ideas, technologies and ways to make your web design look attractive and the idea behind keeping the users stick to your website is to convert them into leads. You can only make it happen when your web design is appealing. To learn more, you can <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">explore us</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/July2022/rVgeqCM12WtigUsrepFx.webp', 'website-redesign-2022-boost-traffic-and-sales-with-these-redesigning-tips', 'Website Redesign 2022 | Cynosure Designs', 'Web designers have taken a shift and have started creating sites as art. The idea behind keeping the users stick to your website is to convert them into leads.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-07-29 10:22:00', '2022-07-29 10:25:27', 4),
	(21, 3, NULL, 'What Metaverse is?', 'Metaverse is a decentralized virtual world platform based on blockchain technology.', '<p>What is Metaverse Technology, and what is this project about? Is it about creating an open platform where people can easily share their content with others and interact in social communities? How is it going to benefit us in the long-term? There are many questions alike. Therefore we are sharing this blog to answer your every question. So let&rsquo;s get started!</p>\r\n<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#whatIsMetaverse">What Is the Metaverse, Exactly?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#do_metaverse_exist">Are Metaverse and Internet the Same?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#access_metaverse">How do I access the Metaverse for now?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_can_metaverse_do">What can you do in the Metaverse?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#make_money_in_metaverse">How to make money in the Metaverse?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#hologram_metaverse">Can Holograms be used in the Metaverse?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#metaverse_today">Metaverse Today</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#future_of_metaverse">Future of Metaverse</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="whatIsMetaverse">What Is the <span class="theme_color">Metaverse</span>, Exactly?</h2>\r\n<p>Metaverse is a decentralized virtual world platform based on blockchain technology. In this virtual world, users can create their content, connect with others, and interact with the environment, overlapping our physical world. This term combines blended digital technologies, including video games, social media channels, emails, video chats, cryptocurrencies, movies, e-books, music, online business, and much more.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Roblox corporation owns Metaverse, encompassing a wide range of concepts. The term Metaverse originated from two words, i.e., &ldquo;Meta&rdquo; and &ldquo;Universe,&rdquo; referring to the digital or 3D world that you can navigate using Augmented Reality (AR) and Virtual Reality (VR). Blockchain games, Non-Fungible Token (NFTs), and crypto payments aren\'t just for crypto geeks, but now they all are accessible as part of an evolving metaverse. You can see metaverse elements in today&rsquo;s popular virtual games, including Roblox, Second Life, Minecraft, and Fortnite.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/1-metaverse.webp" alt="people talking to each other wearing VR" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Are Metaverse and Internet the Same?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>The answer is no. The relationship between the internet and the metaverse is one of the most discussed topics in the industry today. The internet is the infrastructure of the metaverse. It provides a platform for people to meet, socialize, and explore the metaverse. The internet also serves as a foundation for the metaverse to operate on.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/2-Metaverse-and-Internet.webp" alt="people connected via internet" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read More:</strong>&nbsp;<a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/how-are-the-tiktok-algorithms-working-in-2022">How are the TikTok Algorithms working in 2022?</a></p>\r\n<h2 id="do_metaverse_exist">Does Metaverse exist already?</h2>\r\n<p>To some extent, maybe yes, but still in its infancy stage. One thing is sure about Metaverse&mdash;we\'re all about to become very familiar with the immersive 3D experiences. As virtual reality is a transformative technology that could change everything we know about how we interact with the world around us and, in some ways, already have. While there are no guarantees that VR will ever reach the mainstream, it\'s a safe bet that the public will interact with a new array of digital worlds over the next few years.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/3-does-metaverse-exist-already.webp" alt="person standing wearing VR glasses" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="access_metaverse">How do I access the Metaverse for now?</h2>\r\n<p>The metaverse is an entirely different dimension than our present reality that provides us with the capacity to explore the digital universe for ourselves or others to live out in the virtual realm without restriction, as long as you have your computer system and internet connection. The Users can gain access quickly to the metaverse by making their Avatars using the site. Decentraland also allows you to design individuals&rsquo; avatars through their website. Decentraland is a blockchain-based virtual reality platform similar to Second Life. You can purchase plots of land using cryptocurrency and build your world. These platforms are among the most effective and simple methods to access the metaverse.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="what_can_metaverse_do">What can you do in the Metaverse?</h2>\r\n<p>The metaverse is something that is no longer restricted to your computer screen or smartphone. There are many ways to interact with this future version of the internet: through augmented reality headsets, holograms projected into our living rooms, or immersed in a digital environment. Discover what you can do in Metaverse:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/4-what-can-you-do-in-metaverse.webp" alt="person running in a game" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Create Avatar</h3>\r\n<p>You can create an avatar of yourself in the Metaverse at any time. You can choose the gender, name, appearance, and even voice. If you want to make them look unique, you can upload a picture of yourself as their avatar.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Play Video Games</h3>\r\n<p>There are many games to play in the Metaverse. You can play video games alone or by inviting your friends as the games are to relax, have fun, learn something new, or compete with others.</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Socialize and Meet People</h3>\r\n<p>The Metaverse is filled with people from all over the world. You can talk to them, hang out with them, or say hi. You can also join groups of people who share similar interests.</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Watch Movies</h3>\r\n<p>Metaverse is an excellent source for watching movies. You can watch movies anywhere, anytime, and with anyone; that is a perfect way to relax.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Listen to music</h3>\r\n<p>Music is always playing somewhere in the Metaverse. Whether it\'s a radio station, a playlist on Spotify, or Soundcloud, you\'ll never run out of options.</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Online Education</h3>\r\n<p>Metaverse is an online social network that provides a platform for creating, discussing, and sharing knowledge in real-time, using video chats like Skype, Zoom, Google Meet etc. It is designed to focus on education, collaboration, discussion, and development of ideas by all members regardless of background or skills level.</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Online shopping</h3>\r\n<p>Shopping is a popular activity in the Metaverse. People shop and purchase a variety of items from online stores. Shops sell items ranging from apparel, weapons, and more products that every user needs.</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Explore</h3>\r\n<p>The Metaverse is full of different things to explore. There are many places to go, people to meet, and things to experience virtually.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="make_money_in_metaverse">How to make money in the Metaverse?</h2>\r\n<p>Metaverse (MV) is a virtual universe where users can create their avatars and interact with each other in various activities. These activities include socializing, shopping, playing games, and many others. Listed below are some of the sources to make money on metaverse:</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/5-money-in-the-metaverse.webp" alt="Virtual Reality" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Create a Virtual Currency</h3>\r\n<p>Virtual currencies are digital assets that exist only online. Many virtual currencies exist, including Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin, Dogecoin, etc. Virtual currencies have no physical representation, unlike traditional currencies. Instead, they are represented by codes that use cryptography to secure transactions and verify ownership. The Metaverse runs on the technology of blockchain and digital currency called &ldquo;ether.&rdquo; It allows users to buy, sell and trade goods and services using ether, the native currency of this virtual environment, a type of <a href="https://www.kaspersky.com/resource-center/definitions/what-is-cryptocurrency">cryptocurrency</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Sell items on Metaverse</h3>\r\n<p>You can sell anything in the marketplace called the Metaverse Market. If you want to sell something yourself, you need to upload pictures of the item, set its price, and then wait for buyers to contact you. The first thing you should do when getting into selling on the market is to familiarize yourself with the process; this will help you get things done faster and more efficiently, and it will also increase the chances of selling something for a decent profit, instead of losing money.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Metaverse Real Estate</h3>\r\n<p>The land parcels, also called properties in Metaverse&rsquo;s blockchain ecosystem, can be purchased and sold through a NEP-5 token (MKR) app. Users can also earn income by renting out their land parcels to other network users in exchange for MKR tokens. The real estate market has been on the rise across many countries for quite some time now because owning a house can be considered one of the safest investments around the world, especially when it comes to keeping from inflation. If you have a plot of land, you can rent it out and receive a monthly payment.</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Play to Earn Games</h3>\r\n<p>Yes! You read that right. Play to earn is a game where players can make money by completing tasks, watching ads, buying, selling, or simply spending time in the game. There are different types of currencies in the game, and players can earn additional income by performing various tasks. You can start earning points that can be redeemed for rewards, including gift cards, merchandise, and even cash!</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Become a Freelancer</h3>\r\n<p>Freelancing is becoming increasingly popular in the metaverse, especially after Covid-19. Freelance services are online platforms where people can offer their skills and expertise to others via the internet. In Freelancing, you may provide writing, programming, website design, consulting, technical support, translation, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing">digital marketing</a>, public relations, editing, coaching, accounting, and many more services. Freelancing is a great way to earn money online, and you can do it anywhere where there\'s an internet connection, at any time, according to your ease.</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">Open an Art Gallery</h3>\r\n<p>The Metaverse art gallery allows users to view artwork created by designers or artists. Users could purchase artwork online that they find exciting and display it in their homes. Art galleries can have different paintings, sculptures, and other art pieces. Once you have opened up your art gallery online, you need to start selling your work by figuring out how much you want to charge per piece. There are many ways to sell your work, including the <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">development of website</a>, email marketing or social media marketing.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read More:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/what-are-the-7-types-of-digital-marketing">What are the 7 Types of Digital Marketing?</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="hologram_metaverse">Can Holograms be used in the Metaverse?</h2>\r\n<p>Holograms are another gateway to the metaverse. Holographic technology is a type of holography that uses computer-generated images to produce three-dimensional (3D) images. These images are created using femtosecond lasers, which make interference patterns that give off the illusion of depth. In the case of virtual reality, these images are displayed on a screen that the user wears on their head.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Holograms offer more options in metaverse than avatars. Holograms are also being used to create virtual reality experiences. Holographic displays have made significant leaps in recent years, with 3D video content becoming more readily available and accessible across multiple devices, including traditional 2D displays and VR headsets. Holograms are even used to make holographic films that resemble real-life scenes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/6-holograms.webp" alt="A man Standing wearing VR" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="metaverse_today">Metaverse Today</h2>\r\n<p>The metaverse is not dead; it is just in its development stage. We have seen significant progress over the last few years, but we still have a long way to go before getting to where we want to be. We are currently working on the second iteration of the protocol, and this version will take us to our ultimate goal: the &ldquo;metaverse&rdquo; of true decentralization, where anyone can participate at any time, anywhere in the world. This would be a much more significant change than we\'ve seen before, as companies like Amazon or Walmart have locked up the real world of physical assets for years. Now we are entering a new era in which everyone will be able to connect to their virtual economies and share ownership of these virtual worlds.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="future_of_metaverse">Future of Metaverse</h2>\r\n<p>We believe that the future of the metaverse is bright. With metaverse, a user could explore different planets and locations in VR without ever having to leave their home or even a comfortable position on Earth, for that matter! The metaverse as perceived now is a large and complex system built upon multiple technologies and platforms ranging from AR to IoT to VR to 3D experiences and beyond! The idea of creating a virtual universe or metaverse has been around since the 1970s, but there have been few attempts to achieve this over the years.</p>\r\n<p>How will the future Metaverse differ from the current Internet? A new Metaverse will use <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/3D_modeling">3D models</a> instead of 2D images and text on web pages to navigate content and build applications:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You will be able to walk through virtual worlds that you create and share with others.</li>\r\n<li>Can interact with your friends&rsquo; avatars as if they were real people.</li>\r\n<li>Can send your avatar into a virtual space where it can play games or do other things, such as write messages back to you.</li>\r\n<li>Download virtual objects like clothing and jewelry and place them onto your avatar&rsquo;s body.</li>\r\n<li>Able to view the &ldquo;backstage&rdquo; of a website or blog, how it was created, and where it comes from.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/7-future-of-metaverse.webp" alt="3d Person connected to future" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts!</h2>\r\n<p>Ultimately by combining augmented reality with virtual reality, the two concepts will merge into one super-realistic experience that can offer a new way to interact with computers in everyday life. It&rsquo;s only a matter of time, and we&rsquo;ll see what happens in the future as this technology continues to evolve! But metaverse has a long way to go before it is fully optimized.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong class="theme_color">Metaverse, the Virtual World of Reality. Let&rsquo;s live in the Future!</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/ai-in-analytics-helps-in-deep-customer-insights">AI in Analytics helps in deep customer insights</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/August2022/uJz0jnm8RDXpQGIayDSZ.webp', 'what-metaverse-is', 'What Metaverse is? | Blog | Cynosure Designs', 'The combination of AR and VR, the two concepts will merge into one super-realistic experience that can offer a new way to interact with computers.', 'PUBLISHED', 1, 0, '2022-08-05 09:30:00', '2022-08-05 10:30:42', 6),
	(22, 3, NULL, 'What is UI/UX Design? Everything You\'re Wondering About!', 'UI/UX design is the foundation of an effective website or an application.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#user_exp_design">What is User Experience (UX) Design? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#user_interface">What is user interface (UI) design? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ui_vs_ux">UI Vs UX </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#work_together">How They Work Together </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#importance_ui_ux">Importance of UI/UX </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#good_ui_ux">What Makes a Good UX and UI Design? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ui_designer">What Does a UI/UX Designer Do? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#nutshell">In a Nutshell</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">UI/UX has played a vital role in advancing product development and has become a hallmark of that purpose. UI/UX design is the foundation of an effective website or an application. If you want to create a great, engaging, and useful website for your business, then you must be aware of the importance of <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX design</a> and its role in website creation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="user_exp_design">What is User Experience (UX) Design?</h2>\r\n<p>UX refers to the overall experience of an individual using a website, system or an application. Especially regarding individuals\' ease of use, navigating a product, and interaction with the content displayed. User experience is the sum of all interactions between a person and a system/product/service. It includes the physical aspects of the interaction, e.g., touch, sight, and sound, as well as the cognitive and emotional aspects, e.g., ease of learning and usefulness.</p>\r\n<p>UXD-User Experience Design is about understanding people\'s behavior and motivations and then using those insights to create experiences that are intuitive, useful, and delightful. User experience designers can also modify existing products based on user feedback. A good user experience optimized for digital products and services improves their performance and marketability as customers will positively react to them. Successful user experiences are tailored toward the specific needs of individuals, based on their preferences, interests, traits, personas, etc.</p>\r\n<p>Experienced UX designers use a wide range of specialized <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/software-development">software applications</a> to plan, prototype, test, document, publish and market their designs. For instance, digital communication application facilitate face-to-face meetings between business owners and clients in real-time &mdash; all thanks to UX-designed platform such as Skype. Discussed below are the three main approaches used in user experience design.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>1. User-Centered Approach:</h3>\r\n<p>this term was introduced by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_Norman">Don Norman</a>, the father of UX, who defined it as "designing things for people rather than designing things around people." The user-centered design focuses on the end user and asks questions such as: What do they want? How might they use it? Why would they use it? And how should we make it easier for them to get what they need?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>2. User Research:</h3>\r\n<p>the method of gathering information about potential users of a product or service. It involves observing actual users in their natural environment, asking them questions, and analyzing the data collected.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>3. Usability Testing:</h3>\r\n<p>the technique used to evaluate the usability of a website or software application. It involves having participants perform tasks while being observed by researchers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/1-user-experience.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/the-top-3-ux-design-trends-for-2022">The Top 3 UX Design Trends for 2022</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="user_interface">What is User Interface (UI) Design?</h2>\r\n<p>The User Interface Design refers to the look and feel of an application or a website, encompassing the layout screen, typography, color theme, menus, buttons, icons, and other visual elements you interact with. UI designers excel at designing intuitive user interfaces that are easy to understand and navigate without errors or interruptions. Designs must be simple enough for users with limited technical knowledge to understand easily without help from developers or technical support personnel. The compatible designs make the users complete their tasks quickly and efficiently without slowing down systems or consuming excessive storage space.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/2-user-interface.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>User interface (UI) designers create beautiful apps and websites that are easy for users to understand and navigate using common sense. The UI designs are secured enough to prevent unauthorized access by hackers or other online snoopers. UI professionals understand user interface design theory&mdash; how to apply user interfaces to apps and hardware&mdash; which is essential in creating effective interfaces. The apps such as social media platforms like Facebook, Twitter, and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LinkedIn">Linkedin</a> look great on all major mobile operating systems and incorporate highly-designed UIs.</p>\r\n<p>Companies can <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">hire our UI/UX experts</a> to create customized UI designs for their products or websites. This way, users will not get frustrated by elements not appearing where they expect them or being unable to access functions they need due to poorly designed menus or controls.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="ui_vs_ux">UI VS UX</h2>\r\n<p>User interface and user experience are two design concepts that frequently get confused. However, they involve working closely with software engineers to create useful products. Both user interfaces and user experiences require special expertise. Here we will mention the key differences between UX and UI.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class="table table-bordered">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope="col">UX - User Experience</th>\r\n<th scope="col">UI - User Interface</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Interaction Design</td>\r\n<td>Visual Design</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>User Research</td>\r\n<td>Layouts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Wireframes</td>\r\n<td>Color Palettes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Experience</td>\r\n<td>Appearance</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Informational Flow</td>\r\n<td>Graphic Design</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Focus on Interactions</td>\r\n<td>Focus on Tools</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Useful and Accessible</td>\r\n<td>Content</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Customers Insights</td>\r\n<td>Branding &amp; Guidelines</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Creative Thinking</td>\r\n<td>Systematic Thinking</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Collaborate with UI designer</td>\r\n<td>UI is a Part of UX</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Prototype</td>\r\n<td>Typography</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>User Needs</td>\r\n<td>Business Goals</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A good UI/UX needs to be comfortable for the users and to run an entire operating system. It also has to be intuitive for machines as well as aesthetically pleasing. Both aspects are vitally important in determining how successful a product is.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="work_together">How They Work Together?</h2>\r\n<p>UI and UX designers work together in close collaboration to make sure that all efforts are directed toward the same path toward meeting the user\'s needs and expectations. UI designers are the ones who create the final design for the products and services since the final presentation can have an impact on UX. Since it\'s a collaborative initiative, the two design teams work together to create the user interface and experience. In the development process, a UX designer determines how the user interface operates, and the UI designer determines how the user interface appears.</p>\r\n<p>The UI team works on the design, layout, and interface elements that display in a way that is visually appealing to the user\'s eyes. UX designers handle several tasks focused on improving an item for efficient and enjoyable use. Based on the professional\'s experience and team size, one person may be handling these two jobs simultaneously. But, if there is more than one member in these roles, communication between them is essential to the success of a product.</p>\r\n<p>Let\'s suppose that at some point during the design process, additional buttons are required for the screen. This addition could alter how buttons need to be organized and may mean changing their size or shape. The UX team will determine the most effective and easy way to arrange the buttons, while the UI team adjusts their designs to match the latest layout.</p>\r\n<p>Continuous communication and cooperation among UI and UX designers ensure that the user interface is as beautiful as possible while operating smoothly and hassle-free.</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/3-how-they-work.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="importance_ui_ux">Importance of UI/UX</h2>\r\n<h3>Increase ROI</h3>\r\n<p>A good interface design provides your users with easy navigation and engaging content. This makes visitors happy with your <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">website\'s service</a>. Also, satisfied customers will be a source of more conversions as they will also recommend your business to others, i.e., word of mouth. In addition, they will be more loyal to your company and keep coming back. In this way, your Return on Investment will boost.</p>\r\n<h3>Attract and Engage Users</h3>\r\n<p>Before you can generate UI/UX, you need to understand all your customers\' interests. This strategy will make you create a plan to design an interface that will appeal the users and engage them with your displayed content. Additionally, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX services</a> allow you to segment your audience, which is important to understand what your audience wants. Most importantly, understanding users properly can easily convert them into loyal customers. Therefore, your actual sales will increase.</p>\r\n<h3>Elevate your Brand Identity</h3>\r\n<p>Investing in the UI/UX design of the system helps increase consumer satisfaction, which makes customers happy. People love working with brands that satisfy their demands and needs. When satisfied, they help you improve your site by letting you know what features need updating and what additions are needed so far. This increases your company\'s credibility as customers develop a good relationship with your brand. All of these factors help in making your brand&rsquo;s name worldwide.</p>\r\n<h3>User-friendly</h3>\r\n<p>Have you ever wondered why most mobile apps have menus at the bottom instead of the usual desktop top menu? This model is the most popular for a reason. Based on UX research, it makes navigation easier because it stays in the same place no matter what page you\'re viewing. It\'s easier to continue what they want to do on a given screen. The combination of UI/UX services are the perfect solution to make an application or site user-friendly for a specific target market. Most users care about convenience, so a boom of apps and devices has been invented to make your life easier. Therefore, users can browse the application unhindered, leading to the product\'s simplicity, which will likely inform whether the application will succeed.</p>\r\n<h3>Business Growth</h3>\r\n<p>UI/UX focuses on user satisfaction and thus plays an important role in business success. Your product influences a potential customer\'s decision to use your service/product. UI/UX design is important to build brand identity and capture user attention. This lead to business growth and revenue generation and is critical to the company\'s reputation. If a company can implement a user-centric strategy, it will increase customer satisfaction and retention.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="good_ui_ux">What Makes a Good UX and UI Design?</h2>\r\n<p>UX and UI design are essential in any web design, system, software and application. Great user experiences and interfaces make your system easy to use and aesthetically pleasing. Strong UX skills allow you to understand users\' needs and create an intuitive user interface. Good UI design is based on solid engineering principles that ensure your application functions as intended. Experienced UX designers know how to work with engineers to create a stable product. Meanwhile a good UI designer should have a solid understanding of the whole design process. And the planning skills will allow the UX designer to clearly articulate the goals for a new project or app interface.</p>\r\n<p>Planning how users will interact with your designs is crucial for creating truly intuitive applications and websites for the public eye. Good communication skills with clients and project team members are also important traits of a successful UI designer. Many designers have varying opinions on what makes a good UX and UI design. Here are some opinions on the subject from leading industry professionals.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/4-uiux.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>UX - User Experience Elements</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Usable: </strong>website or application must be easy and simple to use.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Useful: </strong>content must be helpful and original to fulfill the needs and requirements.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Accessible: </strong>content must be easily accessible by the users to engage them.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Findable: </strong>users must be able to find easily what they are looking for.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Credibility: </strong>able to gain users\' trust and loyalty with the brand.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Desirable: </strong>content must be attractive and desirable to gain users\' attention.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>UI - User Interface Elements</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Prioritize the appearance and layout of the interface</li>\r\n<li>Encompassed with language, color theme, typography, images, videos, and other visual elements.</li>\r\n<li>Focus on the usability and accessibility</li>\r\n<li>Seamless interaction with the content</li>\r\n<li>Include components like:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Input Components: </strong>toggles, buttons, checkboxes, list boxes, radio buttons, dropdown lists, text fields, etc.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Navigational Components: </strong>icons, tags, pagination, slider, search field, etc</li>\r\n<li><strong>Informational Components: </strong>notifications, message boxes, tooltips, progress bar, modal windows, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="ui_designer">What Does a UI/UX Designer Do?</h2>\r\n<p>If you like the idea of creating awesome user experiences but see yourself as a more visual person, you may be more interested in UI design. You\'ll find a brief snapshot of the key tasks below or a more comprehensive explanation of what a UI/UX designer does in this blog.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Designers use a method of gathering, analyzing, and translating both qualitative and quantitative user data into actionable insights.</li>\r\n<li>Create user-centered designs by understanding business needs, the voice of the customer, user journeys, customer feedback, and usability results.</li>\r\n<li>Completely understand the motivations, needs, and problems of the people who will use your design. If you want the result to be functional and meaningful, it must be built with empathy. Forget about yourself. Listen and understand what your users want.</li>\r\n<li>Quickly and iteratively create user flows, wireframes, prototypes, and low-fidelity and high-fidelity mockups to give you and your team a better idea of what the final product will look like. The UI designer will add visual or interface elements at this stage.</li>\r\n<li>Communicate with the engineering teams as well as stakeholders and executives. While making sure the voice of the customer is present by incorporating customer feedback, usage metrics, and usability survey results into the design.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/5-uiux-designers.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="nutshell">In a Nutshell</h2>\r\n<p>Cynosure Designs can create the bespoke UI/UX designs for the application, website, system and software that help to win the consumers\' confidence and provide them with what they are looking for. The number of customers you get on your website/application can measure great UI and UX success. A satisfied customer is mostly like to stay a loyal customer of the brand. We ensure a good review from a happy client that will increase the credibility of your business. Ultimately, all these factors will lead your business\'s optimal growth and success and help raise the brand value.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Designers work hard to make interaction with technology easy and enjoyable for everyone! </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/boost-your-business-multifold-through-an-optimized-ui-ux-design">Boost your Business Multifold through an Optimized UI/UX Design</a></p>', 'posts/August2022/WjmCYRJY96XIoZY9OaUc.webp', 'what-is-ui-ux-design', 'What is UI/UX Design? | Blog | Cynosure Designs', 'Cynosure Designs’ in-house team has the expertise to create effective and engaging UI/UX designs for the application, website, and system that help to gain the users\' attention.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-08-25 05:52:00', '2022-08-25 07:05:49', 7),
	(23, 3, NULL, 'Build a Brand- A Complete Guide', 'Brand building is developing a unique identity by promoting your business or brand.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#brand_building">What is Brand Building?</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#power_of_brand">The Power of a Brand Name</a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#steps_for_brand_bulding">Steps for a Successful Brand Building Process</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#identify">1. Identify Your Target Audience </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#define">2. Define Your Brand </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#choose_name">3. Choose a Name for your Brand </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#competition">4. Competition Analysis </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#create_vision">5. Create a Vision Statement </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#develop_mission">6. Develop a Mission Statement </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#determine_marketing">7. Determine Your Marketing Strategy </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#build_website">8. Build a Website </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#nutshell">In a Nutshell</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id="overview">The concept of the brand is defined by its name, logo, tagline, color theme, design, and advertising campaign. Branding is a way of making consumers aware of a company\'s products and services. A brand is a promise to the consumer. Consumers want to know what they\'re buying and have specific questions while purchasing anything from the brand, like how long it will last and whether it will meet their expectations. Consumers expect certain things from the brand when they buy a product or service. If those expectations aren\'t satisfied, then the consumer may feel disappointed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="brand_building">What is Brand Building?</h2>\r\n<p>Brand building is developing a unique identity by promoting your business or brand. A brand is what people think about when they hear your name. It\'s how you make yourself memorable. To build a strong brand, you need to create a clear message that resonates with your target audience if you want to stand out from the crowd and get noticed.</p>\r\n<p>The <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding">branding services</a> of a reputable branding agency can build your brand, generate more leads and boost sales. Companies spend millions of dollars each year on branding campaigns. The most crucial element in brand building is understanding who you are trying to reach. What is your target audience? What do they care about? What motivates them? What problems does your product solve? These questions help you develop a strategy for communicating your brand.</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/1-what-is-brand-building.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Reads: </strong><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/what-is-branding-and-how-it-helps-in-business">What is branding and how it helps in business</a></p>\r\n<p>Once you have a plan, you need to put it into action. Today the most popular methods include advertising, public relations, direct mail, word-of-mouth, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">social media marketing</a> , and many other promotion channels. To create a successful brand, ensure you\'re doing things that matter to your customers. If you\'re not getting feedback, you\'re probably not doing anything right. Keep testing until you find something that works.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="power_of_brand">The Power of a Brand Name</h2>\r\n<p>The company\'s trademark that symbolizes its products and services is associated with the power of the brand\'s name. Brands have become increasingly popular over the past years, especially among consumers who want to buy quality products at affordable prices. When purchasing a product, people often choose brands they know and trust. Some people prefer to buy branded goods rather than generic ones. In today\'s world, however, companies use various <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/marketing-strategy">marketing strategies</a> to communicate their message.</p>\r\n<p>Branding is considered essential to help companies build customer engagement and loyalty. Customers associate specific brands with good service and quality products. As a result, they tend to buy the same brands repeatedly. Moreover, many people believe that if a product comes with a well-known brand name, then it must be safe and reliable. Therefore, companies that invest in branding can increase sales and profits.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">connect with Cynosure Designs</a> , the U.K based Brand Design Agency, to get the most out of the best brand designs for you.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/2-power-of-brand-name.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="steps_for_brand_bulding">Steps to a Successful Brand Building Process</h2>\r\n<p>Building a successful brand is a challenging process but can be extremely rewarding. Brands have the power to make money and gain public trust. Understanding the concepts of branding is essential for achieving success in this field. Successful brands are memorable and use a consistent message across all media channels. Considering these steps helps create a fantastic brand that customers can engage with.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="identify">1. Identify Your Target Audience</h3>\r\n<p>The first step in any brand-building process is identifying who your target audience is. Who do you want to reach? What demographic do you want to attract? Where do they live? What are their interests? What are their hobbies? What types of products do they use? These are just some examples of questions to help identify your target audience. Once you have placed your target audience, you need to determine what they want and how you can give them what they are interested in.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/how-to-reach-the-right-audience-with-digital-marketing">How to Reach the Right Audience with Digital Marketing</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="define">2. Define Your Brand</h3>\r\n<p>Once you have determined your target audience, you can define your brand\'s purpose. As a brand is "a name, term, design, symbol, or other feature that identifies one seller\'s goods and distinguishes them from others." When someone hears the word <a href="https://www.starbucks.com">"Starbucks</a>," or sees the logo of Starbucks, they immediately think of coffee. To create a successful brand, you need to define what your brand stands for. Do you want to be known for being environmentally friendly? Do you want to be seen as a reliable business partner? Do you like to offer high-quality products at affordable prices? All of these are great ways to describe your brand.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/3-define-your-brand.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 id="choose_name">3. Choose a Name for your Brand</h3>\r\n<p>After you have decided on the purpose of your business, you need to choose a name for your brand. Choosing a name for your brand is extremely important because it sets the tone for everything else that comes after. If you choose a name that sounds generic or does not suit the business, no matter how well you market your brand, people won\'t remember it. On the other hand, if you pick a catchy or interesting name, people will still remember it even if you don\'t market your brand correctly.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="competition">4. Competition Analysis</h3>\r\n<p>Competitor research can help your organization get an accurate idea of the trends happening in the marketplace that you could have missed otherwise. Identifying trends and predicting future movements can be a huge asset for any business. Competition analysis is an essential component that you should constantly be doing. This strategic research will enable you to review the information about rival firms. It\'s a crucial tactic in finding out what your competitors are doing and what kind of threats you can face during your success.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/4-competitive-analysis.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 id="create_vision">5. Create a Vision Statement</h3>\r\n<p>A vision statement describes precisely what you want your brand to stand for. It helps you focus on where you want your brand to go rather than where you have been. An excellent example of a vision statement would be " We will continue to provide our customers with high-quality products at affordable prices while maintaining a positive environmental impact."</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="develop_mission">6. Develop a Mission Statement</h3>\r\n<p>A mission statement explains why you want to build your brand. This statement explains to potential customers why you exist and what you hope to accomplish. An excellent example of this would be, "Our goal is to provide our customers with the highest quality products at the lowest possible price. We believe that we can achieve this goal by providing superior customer services and offering only the best products available." It is often used in conjunction with a vision statement.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="determine_marketing">7. Determine Your Marketing Strategy</h3>\r\n<p>Now that you have a clear idea of your brand and why you want to build it, you need to decide how you plan to market it. There are many different marketing strategies that you can choose from, including direct mail, radio advertising, PPC, television advertisements, print ads, social media marketing, etc. You need to consider each option carefully before choosing one for your business.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="build_website">8. Build a Website</h3>\r\n<p>Your website is the online face of your business brand. When people hear about any brand, they first try to search for the brand\'s official website. It represents the authenticity of your business and serves as the place where people learn about your company and find out what you offer. Therefore, you must hire an agency to develop a professional-looking website for your brand to make your business recognized worldwide. Make sure your site is user-friendly and mobile responsive, meaning it looks good on smartphones, tablets, and laptops. Also, ensure that your site loads fast so that users aren\'t forced to leave your page and look for another.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/5-build-a-website.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="nutshell">In a Nutshell</h2>\r\n<p>Building a successful brand requires dedication and the most appropriate strategic plans. The <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding">creative branding agency</a> can assist your brand by providing beneficial outcomes. Companies that fail to invest in branding services miss out on a huge opportunity. Consumers are becoming increasingly conscious about what they wear, use and eat. Companies should consider consulting a branding strategist to ensure that their brand identity remains solid and reputable worldwide.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>By remembering these tips, any brand could develop a solid reputation! </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>More Interested Read: </strong><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/six-types-of-branding-services">Six Types of Branding Services</a></p>', 'posts/August2022/Ky6USktBWECBbyznKlnI.webp', 'build-a-brand-a-complete-guide', 'What is Brand Building? | Blog | Digital Agency | Cynosure Designs', 'U.K based branding agency, Cynosure Designs ensures that your brand identity remains strong and reputable around the globe with its branding strategies.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-08-30 10:01:00', '2022-08-30 10:04:31', 5),
	(24, 3, NULL, 'What is Branding and How It helps in business?', 'Branding is the marketing practice of promoting a specific product, service, or brand.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#branding">Branding &ndash; the basics </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_is_branding">What is Branding? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#impacts_of_branding">What are the impacts of Branding? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_is_brand">What is a Brand? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#brand_matters">How Brand matters? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#brand_importance">How is Branding important? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#branding_terms">Key Branding Terms to Know </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#rebranding">The Time For Rebranding </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#strong_brands">Characteristics of Strong Brands </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id="branding">Branding &ndash; the Basics</h2>\r\n<p>If the explanation of branding was simple, there would not be so much ambiguity regarding this concept. Still, for the most part, a strong understanding of branding requires a decent grasp of business, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/marketing-strategy"> marketing strategy</a>, and even basics. Branding is such a vast concept that its definition genuinely encompasses everything it represents and would not bring too much clarity to the subject. But, to lower the incorrect and incomplete information about branding, we are writing this blog in detail.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="what_is_branding">What is Branding?</h2>\r\n<p>Branding is the marketing practice of promoting a specific product, service, or brand. It is a strategy designed by organizations to help people quickly identify and experience the brand. It gives them a reason to choose their products and services over the competitors by clarifying what this particular brand is about.</p>\r\n<p>The process of branding creates a name, symbol, or other feature that identifies a company and distinguishes it from other companies. With the <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding">best branding services</a> , you can appeal to many people and make them feel more connected to your company. Consumers want to feel connected to companies on whom they rely. Customers expect to receive something back when they buy a product or service. If they don\'t get what they need or desire, they may choose to purchase from someone else.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/1-what-is-branding.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="impacts_of_branding">What are the impacts of Branding?</h2>\r\n<p>Branding is a way to identify yourself to others. It\'s a way to tell people who you are and what you stand for. Your brand is how you want people to perceive you. If you have a negative perception of yourself, you will not be able to build a positive image of yourself in front of others. You\'ll always get stuck at the bottom of the ladder. There are some useful impacts of branding strategy:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is a great way to get noticed. </strong>When you put your name out there, you will attract attention. People will know who you are and start looking for you.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is an excellent way to make money.&nbsp; </strong>You can charge more for your products when you have a strong brand. You can even sell your products by yourself without having to go to a distributor.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is a powerful tool. </strong>You can use branding to influence people\'s opinions about you and your business.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is a long-term investment. </strong>You need to invest time and effort into building a brand. You may not see results immediately, but if you keep working on it, you\'ll eventually reap the rewards.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is a reflection of your values. </strong>What you believe in will show in your brand. If you don\'t believe in something, then you shouldn\'t be selling it.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is a representation of your business. </strong>You should represent your company well.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is a sign of trustworthiness. </strong>If you\'re trustworthy and reliable, then people will buy from you.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Branding is a tool for success. </strong>If you\'re successful, then you\'ll have a stronger brand identity.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/2-impact-of-branding.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="what_is_brand">What is a Brand?</h2>\r\n<p>A brand is a word that describes a product\'s name, logo, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/printing-packaging-solution">packaging design</a> , advertising campaign, and any other distinguishing characteristics. A brand is often associated with a company\'s reputation, products, services, and values.</p>\r\n<p>The crucial step in making a brand name is that you\'ll need to build a brand personality. What does your brand stand for? How would people describe your brand? What makes your brand different from others? These questions will help you determine your brand\'s tone, style, and voice. Your brand message should reflect your company\'s mission statement and core values. Ensure your brand messaging is consistent across all channels (e.g. website, social media, print ads, etc.)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="brand_matters">How does Brand matter?</h2>\r\n<p>Brands have become increasingly important and influential in today\'s world as people have become brand conscious. Therefore, consumers want to know who they buy from and how reputable the company is. Brands design companies create a unique identity for your business. They can help differentiate your company from its competitors and provide consumers with a sense of trust and reliability. Consumers want comfort, peace of mind, quality, loyalty, and value for money in the name of the brand they wish to purchase.</p>\r\n<p>When establishing your brand, you need to understand who your target audience is. Once you know your target market, you can start developing a strategy to reach them. It would help if you consider how your brand fits into the marketplace and whether it aligns with your core values. The brand is so important that companies often trademark their products and services to protect them from being copied by others.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/logo-defines-your-brand">Logo Defines Your Brand</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/3-what-is-brand.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="brand_importance">How is Branding important?</h2>\r\n<p>The importance of branding is that it helps companies build credibility where customers feel confident about purchasing from that company. An excellent example of branding is <a href="https://www.apple.com">Apple Inc</a>., which does not directly market its products. Instead, Apple sells its products indirectly through third-party retailers to avoid negative associations with its brand. Following are the key points of the importance of branding.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Business Identity </strong> Branding is one of the most important aspects of any business. A company\'s brand is more important than you think. On the outside, your branding may appear to consist only of things like logos and colors, but your branding is your complete business identity. <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding">Branding services</a> are critical to any business because of their overall impact on your company. Branding can change how people perceive your brand; it can drive new customers and increase brand value &ndash; but it can also do the opposite if done wrongly or not.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Consult our <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">branding strategist</a> today!</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Edge over Competition </strong>Branding can help you differentiate your business from other competitors. It involves developing and implementing several identifiable features for your business so your consumers can associate themselves with your business. Branding increases your consumers\' recognisability of products and services, giving you that competitive edge within the market.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>New and Retained Customers </strong>Branding can help you attract new customers to your brand. You don\'t just want new customers who recognize your brand and use your business once &mdash; you want to create customers who continue to come back. As branding is not just about marketing; it is also about building a solid relationship between a consumer and a company and turning your loyal customers into retained customers.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Business Value and Reputation </strong>Branding plays a vital role in increasing business value in the market. Reputation is the particular opinion that people have about a company. People talk about their trusted brand and share their views about it. Reputation is built and strengthens with the company\'s growth and success over time. A strong reputation helps build trust between a company and its customers, and eventually, the value of the brand increases.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/six-types-of-branding-services">Six Types of Branding Services</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/4-brand-important.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="branding_terms">Key Branding Terms to Know</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand: </strong>The brand name is what people know you by. Brands make companies recognizable and help them stand out from their competition. Companies create brands to represent themselves, and what they do.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Awareness: </strong>Brand awareness is to make people aware of your brand name, products, and services. A brand is something that people recognize and trust.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Equity: </strong>Brand equity is the value of a company\'s name, products, services, and goodwill. It represents the different ways consumers perceive a particular product or service. High brand equity means that the business is generating higher revenue.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Ambassador: </strong>The brand Ambassador is a person who represents a brand and promotes its products and services. A brand ambassador may have different roles depending on the company\'s objectives.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Management: </strong>represents managing a brand\'s image, reputation, and identity. A brand manager ensures that a company\'s products and services meet consumer expectations and maintain its competitive edge. Brand management includes three major components: marketing, advertising, and public relations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Assets: </strong>refer to the elements associated with the brand, such as trademark, logo, tagline, product designs, packaging, and text that make your brand unique and memorable. Companies use brand assets to help market their products and services to consumers.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Architecture: </strong>Brand architecture is the organizational structure that consists of multiple brands and sub-brands under the parent brand.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Experience: </strong>The way customers experience how they are treated and dealt with by a specific brand is called brand experience. Customers always want to feel comfortable, safe, happy, and confident while shopping.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/5-key-brand-term-to-know.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="rebranding">The Time For Rebranding</h2>\r\n<p>Do you know what Rebranding is? Rebranding is changing the company\'s name, logo, color scheme, tagline, website design, social media profiles, business cards, letterhead, packaging, and even products. Any rebranding project aims to ensure that the new brand identity is consistent across all platforms. To do this effectively, you must clearly understand what a rebranding project entails.</p>\r\n<p>There are many reasons why you might want to rebrand. Whatever the case, if you\'re looking to change something about your brand, you should consider Rebranding. Mentioned below can some of the reasons why you should think of Rebranding.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Business is expanding and evolving.</li>\r\n<li>The industry Is growing at a fast pace.</li>\r\n<li>When realized the brand is outdated</li>\r\n<li>Targeting new audience</li>\r\n<li>Business lacks authenticity</li>\r\n<li>The core audience is changing rapidly</li>\r\n<li>Consumers are looking for something new.</li>\r\n<li>The product/service mix has changed</li>\r\n<li>When a company has a wrong brand name or image.</li>\r\n<li>Companies are producing the same products.</li>\r\n<li>The brand is unable to compete</li>\r\n<li>The company\'s mission and vision changed</li>\r\n<li>When a company merges or acquires</li>\r\n<li>When there is high competition.</li>\r\n<li>The company needs to be innovative and creative.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="strong_brands">The Characteristics of Strong Brands</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Quality Products: </strong>the products that are produced under strict quality control standards. These products should be safe, effective, and reliable.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Brand Recognition: </strong>Brands are recognized by their consumers based on the quality of the products and services they provide. Consumers choose brands based on how well-known the brand is and what kind of reputation the brand has.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Value for Money: </strong>Value refers to the price of a product relative to its quality. The product or service should be worth its price.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Consistency: </strong>the degree to which a company maintains the same quality over time. A consistent company always remains consistent in providing high-quality products and services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Innovation:</strong> the act of coming up with new ideas and developing them into something useful. Innovative companies create new products and services that improve upon existing ones.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Customer Service: </strong>the way a company treats its customers. Good customer service includes promptly responding to questions and complaints, resolving problems effectively, and treating customers respectfully.<br /><br /><br /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/6-strong-brands.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts"><br />Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>The values and fundamentals showcase the true essence of branding in today\'s era. Companies use <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/branding">creative branding agencies</a> to create a connection between people and products. When consumers purchase a product, they associate the company\'s brand with the product, making them feel proud of the company. Cynosure Designs a U.K based digital agency, uses great branding strategies that can make your brand unique and recognizable in the market.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Branding takes your company to the next level to gain a competitive edge! </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>More Interested Reads </strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/6-most-effective-digital-marketing-methods-to-grow-your-local-business">6 Most Effective Digital Marketing Methods To Grow Your Local Business </a></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/digital-marketing-strategies-to-grow-your-business">Digital Marketing Strategies to grow your business</a></p>', 'posts/August2022/nNrzUiCSYLuKiwCYX1vr.webp', 'what-is-branding-and-how-it-helps-in-business', 'What is Branding? | Blog | Digital Agency | Cynosure Designs', 'Cynosure Designs has branding experts that use branding strategies to give your brand identity and value in the market to stay competitive.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-08-30 10:39:00', '2022-08-30 11:44:28', 7),
	(25, 4, NULL, 'What is Social Media Marketing: The Ultimate Guide', 'Social media marketing is the process in which a company promotes its products and services on social media platforms.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#smm">What is Social Media Marketing(SMM)? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#importance_of_smm">Importance Of Social Media Marketing? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#pillars_of_smm">Pillars of SMM </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#whats_the_difference">Digital Marketing vs Social Media Marketing: What&rsquo;s the Difference? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#how_smm_work">How does SMM Work? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#smm_platforms">The best social media marketing platforms </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#smm_tips">Social media marketing tips </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#create_smm">How to create a social media marketing strategy </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id="smm">What is Social Media Marketing(SMM)?</h2>\r\n<p>You might be familiar with the term social media marketing but to make you understand the detailed process of social media marketing and how it benefits you, follow us in this article. Social media marketing is the process in which a company promotes its products and services on social media platforms. Social media platforms are used to reach your targeted audience and bring enough traffic to your website. Initially simple social media pages were used as a tool to display the products but now the whole platform of social media has evolved. Several techniques are now used to attract customers on social media.</p>\r\n<p>Your customers can interact with you on your social media page. You and your customers can know each other through social media. You must keep in mind the nature of your business and research to know which social media platform is used the most for such types of businesses. This will help you in targeting your customers on the right social media page.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/1-what-is-social-media-marketing.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="importance_of_smm">Importance Of Social Media Marketing?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>1- Helps in increasing your brand awareness</h3>\r\n<p>In today\'s world, a large number of individuals use social media, making it tough for a new firm to reach out to its potential clients. It becomes tough to show your presence among so many brands. In this case, social media marketing keeps you from falling behind and failing to be recognized. You\'re probably wondering how that happens. To raise brand recognition, you\'ll need social interactions using social media features such as comments section, sharing, reposting, and saving. You may engage people with your business by adding regular and interactive social media postings, and you can simply drive social media traffic to your online presence by adding links to your website. The links can be added to your posts, bio, or profile information directly.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>2- Leads generation and conversion boosting</h3>\r\n<p>The information of customers such as their contact information is called a lead. By having customers\' information, you can approach them to advertise your business. When it comes to social media, engagement activities help in generating leads. It is simpler to convert these leads into conversions. A conversion occurs when your lead turns into a buying customer. This is achievable because someone is following your page because he/she has an interest in your product or service. If your material is good and your posts are attractive, your followers will like, share, or even contact you about it. This way, you may turn those interested followers into regular consumers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can generate leads via social media by following these points</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>People love participating in polls and creative posts so, make such posts for more engagement</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t forget to make your website&rsquo;s links visible on your social media profiles</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Feel like a celebrity and keep hosting live sessions whenever you launch a new product</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t forget to utilize the market places on social media platforms to sell your products</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>3- Focus on customer relationship building</h3>\r\n<p>Connecting with your social media followers is important because it enables you to build long-term business relations. You can do this easily by interacting with them on your posts by replying to their comments. Your timely and informative response will make the follower believe in your good service and as a result, the customer would want to buy from you.</p>\r\n<p>This will not only help your customers in finding solutions to their problems but it will also help you in knowing what your customers are interested in the most. Having input from your customers can help you produce the things that they like the most.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>4- Helps you stand strong among competitors</h3>\r\n<p>Having an eye on your competitors is extremely important. By only following your competitors&rsquo; moves you can know what products are they working on and which type of tactics they are using to achieve success. Looking at how they are running the campaigns helps you in making your social media campaigns successful by following the dos and don&rsquo;ts on their posts.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/2-importance-of-social-media-marketing.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="pillars_of_smm">Five Core Pillars of Social media marketing</h2>\r\n<h3>1- Social Strategy</h3>\r\n<p>The most important pillar of social media marketing is creating a social strategy. If you plan to make your first impression on your social media page with your first post, make sure you have worked on a social strategy first. The most important thing is how to create a social media strategy. Well, your strategy should be based on your customers. For making a customer-centric strategy, consider the following points first.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>List your goals</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Select the social media platform following your goals</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>What type of content would be attractive to your customers</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>2- Planning &amp; Publishing</h3>\r\n<p>A regular presence on social media is necessary for an online business to keep customers informed about it. To present your brand in front of your customers, you need to plan and publish accordingly and timely.</p>\r\n<p>The things that you will post on your social media accounts will be the turning points for your business. Post a type of content that speaks for you. You can simply post videos and photos or you can simply post some content but what matters the most is to have planned publishing. Consider the following points for that:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Keep an eye on when your customers come online the most</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Keep an eye on your post reach</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Keep an eye on the content quality</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>3- Wait for engagement &amp; listen to your audience</h3>\r\n<p>Everything takes time therefore, your brand will also take time to get recognized. So, the first thing you need to do is be patient with your efforts. Observe around and then plan and implement accordingly. Initially, followers are not so confident about a new brand so they don&rsquo;t engage with you much. To gain their attention you need to make regular postings. In doing so, don&rsquo;t forget to maintain the quality of your posts so that they are not low level.</p>\r\n<p>Once you start posting regularly and intelligently, you will find your followers interacting with you through comments or direct messages. There might also come a time when your followers might tag you in their social posts after buying something from you. But for this, all you need is patience and regularity. The most heartwarming thing for you as a business would be when your customers will start sharing your content.</p>\r\n<p>You can achieve all of this by listening to your customers. When you give importance to each comment and message, it will not only make a good impression on your customers but also will help you in knowing what they are saying. Their feedback will help you grow eventually.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/3-five-pillars-of-social-media-marketing.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>4- Analytics and Reporting</h3>\r\n<p>Metrics are the reports that help you in understanding the progress of your posts. When it comes to online marketing platforms, analytics and reporting are there to help you with it. If you just keep posting and don&rsquo;t observe who is seeing that post and who is interacting with it, it won&rsquo;t be of any use. Without this observation, you might be targeting the wrong audience. The analytics and reports can help you in identifying the right potential customers who keep moving around your posts. So, why not target them directly? Reporting will help you in</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Analyzing the reach difference between previous and current months</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Number of mentions you get in a month</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Knowing who is taking your brand&rsquo;s name</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>What&rsquo;s the number of users who interacted with your posts</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>All information about the new followers</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>5- Ads</h3>\r\n<p>Advertising is the most important thing in social media marketing. If you have learned everything except advertising, you are still not there. We are talking about ads here. Now when you already have done a lot, do a little more and invest in social media ads. It will assist you in connecting with your potential customers. Your posts can reach as many people as you want. The more you will invest in ads, the more your products can reach people. But ads work well when your content and products are good.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="whats_the_difference">Digital Marketing vs Social Media Marketing: What&rsquo;s the Difference?</h2>\r\n<p>Digital marketing is a vast area of marketing that includes Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Pay-per-Click (PPC), Social Media Marketing, Content Marketing, Email Marketing, Mobile Marketing, Marketing Analytics, and Affiliate Marketing. Digital marketing is not limited to social media marketing.</p>\r\n<p>Whereas, social media marketing is the promotion of a business through social media platforms with different techniques such as social media posts displaying the products and telling about the services, through social media stories and reels by making short videos in which the business is explained or a product or service is promoted, by sharing website links to the social media channels via sponsored posts or sponsored stories.</p>\r\n<p>The majority of people are found on social media platforms rather than email inboxes or websites such as Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, LinkedIn, Quora, YouTube, Pinterest, Reddit, Snapchat, etc in abundance. That is why social media marketing is a major subcategory of digital marketing. If we skip social media marketing from <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/">digital marketing</a>, a business or website can fail to attain most of its traffic and the business reach can be much lower resulting in a lower ROI.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/4-digital-marketing-vs-smm.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="how_smm_work">How does Social Media Marketing Work?</h2>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/digital-marketing/smm">Social media marketing</a> works with several things altogether. The majority of people use social media. Social media marketing is more like an online way of selling something just like you would do it in a tangible shop and advertise through billboards about your business and then your regular customers will bring you more customers due to your good behavior, shop presentation, and good quality products. Likewise, your online page is your shop and your posts are your ambiance, while the way you interact and respond to the comments and messages, that creates a way for your loyal customers. So, the following are the <strong>best social media marketing platforms</strong> you can try to start making money from.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="smm_platforms">The best SMM platforms</h2>\r\n<h3>Facebook</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Users: <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/346167/facebook-global-dau/#:~:text=During%20the%20first%20quarter%20of,percent%20of%20monthly%20active%20users.&amp;text=With%20over%202.6%20billion%20monthly,most%20popular%20social%20network%20worldwide.">1.9 billion </a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Audience: Generation X and Millennials</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impactful to: the B2C industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Trending in: Advertising &amp; Brand awareness</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>TikTok</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Users: <a href="https://newsroom.tiktok.com/en-us/1-billion-people-on-tiktok">1 billion</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Audience: Gen Z followed by Millennials</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impactful for: B2C as well as B2B industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Trending in: Short-form creative video content; user-generated content; brand awareness</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Instagram</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Users: <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/253577/number-of-monthly-active-instagram-users/">1 billion</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Audience: Millennials</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impactful to: the B2C industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Trending in: High-quality images, videos &amp; advertising</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Twitter</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Users: <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/970920/monetizable-daily-active-twitter-users-worldwide/">211 million </a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Audience: Millennials</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impactful for: B2C as well as B2B industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Trending in: Public relations; customer service; community building</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>LinkedIn</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Users: <a href="https://www.statista.com/forecasts/1147197/linkedin-users-in-the-world">774 million </a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Audience: Generation X, / Millennials</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impactful for: B2B industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Trending in: B2B relationships, business development, and social selling</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>YouTube</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Users: <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/1252638/youtube-app-dau-worldwide/">315 million daily active </a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Audience: All types</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impactful for: B2B &amp; B2C industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Trending in: Brand awareness; long-form videos and how-to/do-it-yourself videos</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Snapchat</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Users: <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/545967/snapchat-app-dau/#:~:text=With%20an%20estimated%2046%20million,such%20as%20Twitter%20or%20Facebook.">306 million</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Audience: Generation Z</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impactful for: &amp; B2C industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Trending in: Brand awareness; advertising</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/5-best-smm-platform.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="smm_tips">Social media marketing tips</h2>\r\n<p>Each social media platform should be treated uniquely because every platform is different. You should establish a particular and deliberate plan for each platform. You should make these little separate strategies for each platform just like you create a whole big strategy for social media marketing itself. It may not be necessary for your brand to be present on every platform, but for your postings to be targeted, you must have a platform-specific approach.</p>\r\n<p>Keep these things in your mind</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Who will I target by using this platform?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Who has access to this platform?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>What should be the genre of posts for this platform?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Well, if you find it difficult to answer these questions, it is never too late to find better help with a social media marketing company. Let&rsquo;s move on to creating a social media marketing strategy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="create_smm">How to create a social media marketing strategy</h2>\r\n<p>While creating a social media marketing strategy keep the following points in your head and you will end up making the best strategy for yourself.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Be reliable.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Concentrate your message</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Keep an eye on the hottest topics</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Measure and evaluate outcomes</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Spend money on video content</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Participate in communities</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Engage with the audience</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Don\'t let algorithm changes demotivate you</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Associating with micro- and macro-influencers</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Include every team member.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/6-social-media-marketing-strategy.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="final_thoughts">Final Thoughts</h2>\r\n<p>A digital/online way of promoting a business, product, idea, or service to existing and new customers. Digital marketing includes marketing through Google Ads, SEO, PPC, Email Marketing, Content Marketing, Affiliate Marketing, Influencer Marketing, Mobile Marketing, and Social Media Marketing through Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, LinkedIn, Quora, YouTube, Pinterest, Reddit, Snapchat, etc. you can utilize all of these platforms by simply following the tips and techniques discussed above. Or if you don&rsquo;t want to grind your head around these things, simply contact the <strong> best digital marketing company in the UK.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">Contact Us Now!</a></strong></p>', 'posts/August2022/1ZXOxoJv6OYd0qeTn52h.webp', 'what-is-social-media-marketing-the-ultimate-guide', 'What is Social Media Marketing: The Ultimate Guide | Cynosure Designs', 'Social media marketing is the process in which a company promotes its products and services on social media platforms.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-08-30 11:05:00', '2022-08-30 11:42:03', 5),
	(26, 3, NULL, 'What You Should Know About User Experience Design', 'A good user experience makes people happy, keeps them coming back, and encourages them to share their experiences with others.', '<div class="table_of_contents_box">\r\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="table_of_contents">\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#overview">Overview </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_is_ux">What is UX? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#why_ux_matters">Why does UX matter? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#know_about_ux">Things To Know About UX Design </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ux_examples">User Experience Examples </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ux_vs_usability">User Experience vs Usability </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#what_ux_designer">What Does a UX Designer Do? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#ux_design_tools">UX Design Tools? </a></li>\r\n<li><a class="goto_sec" href="#nutshell">In a NutShell </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p id="overview">Do you want your users to feel easy, comfortable and safe while interacting with your system, application, or website? A good user experience makes people happy, keeps them coming back, and encourages them to share their experiences with others. Not just the user, but it also has a positive impact on companies by creating products that customers love and helping them make money. Look no further as we write this blog to give a complete guide about user experience design.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="what_is_ux">What is UX?</h2>\r\n<p>User Experience (UX) is the experience people have while using a company\'s product, service, website, or system. It includes how they feel and interact with a particular product or service, their expectations before using it, and what they think after using it. UX design involves understanding end users\' goals, motivations, ease of use, perceptions, and behaviours and then designing solutions that meet those needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/1-what-is-ux-design.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="why_ux_matters">Why does UX matter?</h2>\r\n<p>UX design does matter as it plays an essential role in how people perceive and interact with things. UX is about understanding what makes users happy and unhappy and how they use technology. A good UX design positively impacts customers\' loyalty and engagement with your system, and a bad UX has a negative effect.</p>\r\n<p>UX is not just about <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/web-development">designing websites</a>; it\'s about ensuring that the user experience is suitable across all devices and platforms. An easy-to-use design enables users to interact with the products easily. For example, if you\'re trying to sell something, you want to make it easy for someone to buy it. You don\'t want them to have to think about how to use your system and what to do. You want them to know exactly what to do and how to do it.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="know_about_ux">Things To Know About UX Design</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>User Research: </strong> The most crucial step in any UX project. It helps designers understand users\' preferences, interests, and behaviours. It\'s also helpful to get feedback from real users before building anything.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Prototyping:</strong> A great way to test ideas and validate assumptions. Before building a genuine product, you can use paper prototypes, wireframes, or interactive mockups.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Usability Testing:</strong> An effective method of evaluating how well a website, application, or system works for its targeted audience. It involves observing people using the site or app and then analyzing their behaviour.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Visual Design:</strong> Includes everything from colors and fonts to images and icons. Good graphic design makes websites and apps look professional and attractive.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Content Strategy:</strong> The process of planning what type of content should be displayed on a website or application. The content must be helpful, informative, and appealing to the users to engage them./p&gt;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>UI and UX: </strong> The user Interface is a part of the User Experience. UI is the set of tools and features that make up a particular user experience. It includes navigation menus, buttons, icons, dropdown lists, and other controls. In contrast, UX is the total of all interactions between a person and a system. This is where <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs"> UI UX design service</a> comes in..</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Information Architecture:</strong> The structure of pages and sections on a website or application, including links, categories, and other navigational elements, which the users can interact with.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Simple, Usable, and Accessible Design:</strong> The design must be easy and simple so that users can understand it to satisfy their needs and requirements. Engaging users is essential; otherwise, a complicated system will make them leave your site.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/2-to-know-about-design.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="ux_examples">User Experience Examples</h2>\r\n<p>A good user experience would be a site that is clean, organized, and easy to navigate. Let\'s take an example of well-known e-commerce website i.e <a href="https://www.amazon.com">Amazon</a>. Where customers find the shopping experience effortless, simple, easy, and hassle-free, many users find Amazon\'s UX as the most appealing one.</p>\r\n<p>Conversely, if the content is lengthy, complex, and complicated, then the user experience will be poor. Sharing another example of a bad user experience of an online marketplace like eBay. eBay provides overloaded complex information on its product pages, making the users confused when making choices.</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/ui-ux-designs">Hire the creative UX design company</a> today to set an example for the best UX design wordwide!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="ux_vs_usability">User Experience VS Usability</h2>\r\n<table class="table table-bordered">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th style="text-align: left;" scope="col">UX</th>\r\n<th style="text-align: left;" scope="col">Usability</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Overall experience of user</td>\r\n<td>Accomplish a specific goal</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Concerned with interaction with the system</td>\r\n<td>Concerned with efficiency and effectiveness</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Refers to happiness of user</td>\r\n<td>Refers to ease-of-use</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Can the user be delightful?</td>\r\n<td>Can user meet the needs and requirments?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Valuable and meaningful</td>\r\n<td>Easy and intuitive</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Did the user enjoy?</td>\r\n<td>Did the user learn?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>What users feel?</td>\r\n<td>What and how users do?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/3-ux-vs-usability.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="what_ux_designer">What Does a UX Designer Do?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>User Experience Designers (UXD) work closely with UI designers, product managers, marketers and developers to create user-centred experiences for digital products.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>UXDs focus on how people interact with technology and design systems that make sense and feel intuitive.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>They collaborate with designers and engineers to understand users\' goals and motivations and translate those insights into usable and engaging designs.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Helps teams identify problems and threats before they become critical issues.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Uses research methods to learn about users and their behaviours, preferences, interests and expectations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Works closely with stakeholders to ensure that the final product meets business objectives.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Works across different platforms and devices to create accessible, valuable and usable experiences.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>They have a broad knowledge of human behaviour, usability, information architecture, interaction design, visual design, and content strategy.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Responsible for developing prototypes and wireframes and may also lead the creation of mockups and interactive presentations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Communicates efficiently and effectively with clients, team members, and management.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Keep themselves up-to-date with current <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/the-top-3-ux-design-trends-for-2022">UX design trends </a> and technologies in the industry.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Maintains professional relationships with peers, vendors, and clients.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Contributes to the success of projects by providing creative solutions to complex challenges.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Provides feedback and suggestions for improvements.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id="ux_design_tools">UX Design Tools?</h2>\r\n<p>As we have discussed that UX is about making things look catchy. To make a design, UX designers utilize multiple tools and technologies. Here we are writing about some of the standard and valuable tools.</p>\r\n<h3>Adobe XD</h3>\r\n<p>Adobe XD is an application for designing prototyping tools. It\'s a powerful tool for designers and developers alike. It can create UI/UX elements and share them across devices.</p>\r\n<h3>Sketch</h3>\r\n<p>A sketch is a software tool for creating wireframes, mockups, prototypes, and user flows. A sketch is an excellent tool for UX designers who want to get their ideas out fast and collaborate easily with others.</p>\r\n<h3>Axure RP</h3>\r\n<p>Axure RP is a product-based solution for rapid prototyping and collaboration. It includes multi-device testing, responsive web design, and interactive prototypes.</p>\r\n<h3>Envision</h3>\r\n<p>Envision is a cloud-based platform that helps teams visualize and prototype their designs. It offers a variety of features, including annotations, smart guides, and collaborative boards.</p>\r\n<h3>Framer X</h3>\r\n<p>Framer X is a powerful tool for building prototypes. It lets you drag and drop components to create interfaces and animations. It supports both Android and IOS applications.</p>\r\n<h3>Balsamiq Mockups</h3>\r\n<p>Balsamiq Mockups is a simple yet powerful tool for creating wireframes and prototypes. It comes with a range of pre-designed templates for different types of projects.</p>\r\n<h3>Marvel App</h3>\r\n<p>Marvel is a mobile application that allows users to create and edit HTML5 prototypes. It provides a range of features, including drag &amp; drop interface builder, animation editor, and code view.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/storage/posts/August2022/4-ux-design-tools.webp" alt="" /></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 id="nutshell">In a NutShell</h2>\r\n<p>Hence, concluded that UX is about making people feel comfortable and engaging them with your design. When our creative design agency design a product or system for you, we make sure that it must be up to the mark. Cynosure Designs also ensures that users feel more relaxed while ensuring that it\'s safe to use. Hopefully, we have guided each aspect of the User experience in this blog. If you think something is missing or cannot catch what you were looking for, <a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/contact-us">contact our UX design experts</a>. We will be glad to help you!</p>\r\n<p>We figure out the best User Experience to make it more beautiful, practical, and fun!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suggested Blogs: </strong><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/blog/boost-your-business-multifold-through-an-optimized-ui-ux-design">What is UI/UX Design? Everything You\'re Wondering About! Boost your Business Multifold through an Optimized UI/UX Design </a></p>', 'posts/September2022/NOGCQsaiyvehbGChHt1e.webp', 'what-you-should-know-about-user-experience-design', 'What is UX? | Blog | UX Design Agency | Cynosure Designs', 'Cynosure Designs creates the attractive User Experience while ensuring that people feel more relaxed and comfortable while using it.', 'PUBLISHED', 0, 0, '2022-09-01 04:53:00', '2022-09-01 04:57:02', 5);
