	(2, 'Stubbee', 'projects/November2021/rGW7U1aknaavpOA4hkK1.png', 'projects/November2021/O7py6Cy8gW3YBf3906rE.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Cynosure re-designed a responsive website of Stubbee. The objective was to create a modern outlook of the website with animations, strong visuals, cinemagraphs and new content. Moreover, the website&rsquo;s layout was designed for a user-friendly experience, keeping in mind the global brand guidelines &amp; consumer journey of the target audience.</p>\r\n<p>Our digital media agency also devised &amp; implemented a viable SEO strategy for Stubbee considering the multiregional nature of the website. Paying keen attention to technical SEO, Cynosure enhanced their brand visibility, monthly traffic sessions &amp; keyword rankings.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/branding">Branding</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'stubbee', 'ACTIVE', 'Stubbee | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Stubbee made the most of our Web Development Solutions to establish a platform for UK and EU region.', '2021-11-17 05:08:01', '2022-01-20 10:21:52', NULL, 0, '#ffdada'),
	(3, 'Bizpad', 'projects/November2021/Qc0zz70PhQLJGkfbKPmD.png', 'projects/November2021/CeCDJrq6qqQobASJCIvc.png', NULL, '<h1>Accountancy Management <br />Software Development</h1>\r\n<p>Cynosure develop accountancy management software for bizpad. The objective was to create a Saas based software with enhanced user experience. Moreover, the Application layout was designed for a user-friendly experience, keeping in mind the global brand guidelines &amp; consumer journey of the target audience.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/software-development">Accountancy Software</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/branding">Branding</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'bizpad', 'ACTIVE', 'Bizpad | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how bizpad made the most of our software Development Solutions to establish a platform.', '2021-11-17 01:05:00', '2021-11-19 04:49:51', NULL, 1, '#e9f7fe'),
	(4, 'Tahira Foods', 'projects/November2021/E56h9Mg5vqgz6LskDHO7.png', 'projects/November2021/5EUgIKOfDm20T2ub55bm.png', NULL, '<h1>Design &amp; Printing solution</h1>\r\n<p>Planned and designed the products for Tahira Foods that collectively is a manufacturer and distributor of food items. The main ultimatum of Tahira Foods is to supply affordable halal foods that attract muslim community in Europe.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/printing-packaging-solution">Printing &amp; Packaging</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/branding">Branding</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'tahira-foods', 'ACTIVE', 'Tahira Foods | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Tahira Foods made the most creative product designs to establish a premier brand for halal products in Western Europe.', '2021-11-19 05:14:14', '2022-01-20 10:23:51', NULL, 0, '#ffebeb'),
	(5, 'Citywide Foods', 'projects/November2021/qoH8KUt497rTgXN4up55.png', 'projects/November2021/tQSQw2UMlcp99g5ogmqu.png', NULL, '<h1>Design &amp; Printing Services</h1>\r\n<p>Offered and transformed business processes of City Wide Food with the ultimate advance solutions of product designing and digital printing in futuristic facets. Upholded the major concerns of brand sustainability and creative packaging with new and innovative ideas.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/printing-packaging-solution">Printing &amp; Packaging</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/branding">Branding</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'citywide-foods', 'ACTIVE', 'Citywide Foods | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how CityWide Foods made creative product designs for food packaging containers.', '2021-11-19 05:32:00', '2022-01-20 10:22:53', NULL, 0, '#dbffe6'),
	(6, 'Secret Pleasure', 'projects/November2021/Gnui2NopXU2hoWZztWEc.png', 'projects/November2021/OzbfsFbMc3EIIUr4lir7.png', NULL, '<h1>Woocommerce Website Development</h1>\r\n<p>Cynosure develop woocommerce responsive website of Secret Pleasure. The objective was to create a modern outlook of the website with animations, strong visuals, and Seo friendly. Moreover, the website is integrated with 3rd party system for products and one click checkout.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX Designs</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'secret-pleasure', 'ACTIVE', 'Secret Pleasure | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Secret Pleasure made the most of our Woocommerce solution to establish a platform for UK and EU region.', '2021-11-24 10:54:48', '2021-11-19 07:12:13', NULL, NULL, '#ffd6dc'),
	(7, 'Success Finders', 'projects/November2021/4VeMTZHW2zKVrWdakfYt.png', 'projects/November2021/y9uLong6zvdHUKCpdng8.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Development</h1>\r\n<p>Success Finders is an initiative set up to support student careers by providing them with the best opportunities to access UK top Ranked Universities. The company was receiving a few applications per month. After the creation of a website with Cynosure Designs, the company started receiving an average of 200 applications per day.</p>\r\n<p>Cynosure designed a responsive website for Success Finders with a user-friendly experience, keeping in mind the Consumer Journey of the target audience. Cynosure delivered the following services:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Conceptualization</li>\r\n<li>Consumer Journey Mapping</li>\r\n<li>Design Framework</li>\r\n<li>Copywriting</li>\r\n<li>Design Layout</li>\r\n<li>Lead Generation Forms</li>\r\n<li>Front-End Design &amp; Development</li>\r\n<li>Technology: PHP, HTML 5, CSS3, Bootstrap</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX Designs</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'success-finders', 'ACTIVE', 'Success Finder | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Success Finder made the responsive website solution to establish a platform for UK and EU region.', '2021-11-19 06:58:51', '2022-06-20 12:49:31', NULL, 0, '#ffebee'),
	(8, 'Joubi', 'projects/November2021/vgdLyk5t3cVODTmMgDDt.png', 'projects/November2021/ohkZktZ4X06X8OwBVosX.png', NULL, '<h1>E-commerce Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>From building a brand to Ecommerce store, we did all for Joubi and overcame the challenges with the mindset to excel in everything and become customers\' first choice with respect to loyalty and trust. Cynosure designed a responsive Magento store for Joubi with a user-friendly experience.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX Designs</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><video class="aligners_work_video" style="object-fit: cover;" preload="auto" loop="loop" controls="controls" width="100%">\r\n                    <source src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/projects/videos/joubi-london.mp4" type="video/mp4" />Sorry, your browser\r\n                    doesn\'t support embedded videos.\r\n                </video></p>', 'joubi', 'ACTIVE', 'Joubi | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Joubi made the creative brand and  E-commerce store.', '2021-11-26 07:49:29', '2021-11-30 03:08:14', NULL, 0, '#ebfff4'),
	(9, 'OTHM', 'projects/November2021/m8lfliTTXtrEMPtjBBQK.png', 'projects/November2021/PNUriug5LajNOGZZ7xbi.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>OTHM selected us for designing and developing their world-renowned institute\'s Website with the ambition to strengthen the British Qualification Standard. Came up with the advanced and innovative technology that raised the students\' expectations, their effectiveness, performance and all the above cognitive ability.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'othm', 'ACTIVE', 'OTHM | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how OTHM made Website & CRM to make the best user experience for their audience', '2021-11-29 07:39:22', '2021-12-07 08:58:39', NULL, 0, '#82c3d3'),
	(10, 'Savayra Foundation', 'projects/November2021/f8FoWye5ekJWNd3sdgJ0.png', 'projects/November2021/OyXWQvbQb6V4AUSEUuR1.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Developed a well-designed and visionary Website and integrated strategies to meet challenges for the Savayra Foundation, running its overwhelming NGO. Provided corresponding solutions to NGO in the manner of strong networking and global identification through a source of effective strategic planning.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'savayra-foundation', 'ACTIVE', 'Savayra Foundation| Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Savayra Foundation made Website to show its global presence.', '2021-11-29 07:51:39', '2021-12-07 08:52:38', NULL, 0, '#f7ecc5'),
	(11, 'Gina Bacconi', 'projects/November2021/Hxwa2wG2Kvr0LByq0tsv.png', 'projects/November2021/AYW7er4A7evLjp4yVH6Q.png', NULL, '<h1>Magento Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Empowered brand identity that increased the likeability of the brand, Gina Bacconi, delivering Apparels and Accessories with a creative E-business channel. Converted visitors into paying customers with secured data identification after the successful competition analysis in the market.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/branding">Branding</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><video class="aligners_work_video" style="object-fit: cover;" preload="auto" loop="loop" controls="controls" width="100%">\r\n                    <source src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/projects/videos/gina-bacconi.mp4" type="video/mp4" />Sorry, your browser\r\n                    doesn\'t support embedded videos.\r\n                </video></p>', 'gina-bacconi', 'ACTIVE', 'Gina Bacconi | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Gina Bacconi made the creative brand and  E-commerce store.', '2021-11-29 07:56:20', '2021-11-30 03:07:50', NULL, 0, '#ffd6dc'),
	(12, 'Regent Park Mosque', 'projects/November2021/cbjI2LC6223ttCVXsI6j.png', 'projects/November2021/ESDKet3z3hggZWxMyyKA.png', NULL, '<h1>Design &amp; Printing Solution</h1>\r\n<p>Our professionals served the U.K leading London Central Mosque, which was established in 1977 for Muslim worship. With the purpose to identify the dominating mosque worldwide, we set up maximum exposure with captivating methodologies to capture the world\'s engagement and interest.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk/services/printing-packaging-solution">Printing &amp; Packaging</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'regent-park-mosque', 'ACTIVE', 'Regent Park Mosque| Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Cynosure Designs work for Regent Park Mosque to design bags.', '2021-11-29 08:14:37', '2022-04-25 07:20:58', NULL, 0, '#8ef0ef'),
	(13, 'London academy Business School (LABS)', 'projects/November2021/cQYGRPAeyfQHADssra17.png', 'projects/November2021/Jp2KJlu9yjHYnFDjdPZA.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Accredited LABS with the bespoke professionally Designed and Developed Website with the motive of adding value in the reputable educational institute. LABS stands out nationwide due to providing quality education, while maintaining core values, standards and dignity.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'london-academy-business-school', 'ACTIVE', 'London academy Business School| Digital Marketing Agency In UK', 'Discover how London academy Business School made Website & CRM to make the best user experience for their students', '2021-11-29 08:21:41', '2022-04-25 13:20:55', NULL, 0, '#afb6ee'),
	(14, 'BluButterfly', 'projects/November2021/9pc4qdidpVlab96XIskg.png', 'projects/November2021/dmZcRo1YJ4QZvsdkYjhp.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Giving an extraordinary and finest experience and clasping the sense of taste behind the bars that drove value for money beverages. Likewise the synthesized and refreshing drinks for the Bar\'s clients, we served BlubButterfly with the new and unique blended concepts, featuring in the Website.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'blu-butterfly', 'ACTIVE', 'BluButterfly | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how BluButterfly cafe made Website to show their menu items to know more about offerings', '2021-11-29 08:32:17', '2021-12-07 08:51:14', NULL, 0, '#a8e4f0'),
	(15, 'London Graduate School', 'projects/November2021/uktgAWtcNKvArMwSvgeZ.png', 'projects/November2021/KdMIGKjyHtv4bHJQEDra.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Awarding students with advanced academic as well as professional degrees in particular fields. Cynosure Designs apprenticed with British London Graduate School to guarantee combining quality and reliability for the next generation in the educational sector.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'london-graduate-school', 'ACTIVE', 'London Graduate School | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how London Graduate School made Website & CRM to make the best user experience for their students', '2021-11-29 08:35:26', '2021-12-07 08:48:17', NULL, 0, '#fba7ac'),
	(16, 'AR Luxury Real Estate', 'projects/November2021/wTKPK6j028YBRAgnWkFg.png', 'projects/November2021/2FlMMHF6RSzZK53lWcuh.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Helped ANKE RICE to build a brand to get more out of Real Estate business for a luxurious lifestyle. The main focus of AR was to set market trends by offering unique property rental services and making a connection between communities.</p>\r\n<p>Cynosure designed a responsive website for AR Luxury Real Estate with a user-friendly experience, keeping in mind the consumer journey to showcase the Luxurious properties designed by ANKE RICE.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'ar-luxury-real-estate', 'ACTIVE', 'AR Luxury Real Estate | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how AR Luxury Real Estate get more out of Real Estate business for a luxurious lifestyle.', '2021-11-29 08:38:31', '2021-12-07 08:45:19', NULL, 0, '#f7f7f7'),
	(17, 'Johns Hopkins', 'projects/November2021/esFulvPYGm0hizwFrqXJ.png', 'projects/November2021/4IYzwC6kBLsrjs6EQDky.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Software Development</h1>\r\n<p>Dedicatedly served Johns Hopkins College in a well being optimistic manner to support the Professionalism and Educational industry. Transitioned and removed the roadblocks to make the College experience as best as it can possibly be.</p>\r\n<p>Cynosure designed a responsive website for Johns Hopkins with a user-friendly experience, Develop a vacancies portal for offering career opportunities to applicants. This platform was designed to immensely build and plan according to recruitment challenges. The Web Application specifically manages the complete hiring process including screening, scheduling, interviewing and selection of prospective candidates that fit in the job description.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/printing-packaging-solution">Printing &amp; Packaging</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/branding">Branding</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'johns-hopkins', 'ACTIVE', 'Johns Hopkins | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Johns Hopkins made the most of our Branding, Printing, and Web Development Solutions to establish an Educational institute in UK.', '2021-11-29 08:42:06', '2021-11-30 03:25:35', NULL, 0, '#c7dbf5'),
	(18, 'Tec Training', 'projects/November2021/ZCKB1IUv1tLdvk7Zgx0t.png', 'projects/November2021/cfEwxFL04Sc6bGwF4lFP.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Development &amp; Printing solution</h1>\r\n<p>The U.K leading institute of Professional Training Courses needed a unique digital strategy to innovate and increase awareness partially with an online outreach approach. With such intention Cynosure Designs\' experts penetrated with quality designed Website and Printing on various products that created an influential impact internationally.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'tech-training', 'ACTIVE', 'Tec Training | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Tec Training made their Website for seamless user experience and brand awareness.', '2021-11-30 06:14:03', '2022-04-25 12:36:10', NULL, 0, '#f2f0b0'),
	(19, 'Mclaren Resourcing', 'projects/November2021/YZgYR3F9AvOqTnFil5N8.png', 'projects/November2021/hare4x2IqBIrzaX7Tx8p.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Development &amp; Printing solution</h1>\r\n<p>As the name specifies, Mclaren Resourcing agency specializes in providing customized Recruitment solutions efficiently to numerous organizations and achieving the targets that business needs. Ensuring availability, standards set, target marketing, products and services visibility, brand loyalty and brand awareness, we helped Mclaren Resourcing with implemented strategies throughout the marketing endorsement.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/printing-packaging-solution">Printing Solution</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'mclaren-resourcing', 'ACTIVE', 'Mclaren Resourcing | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Mclaren Resourcing made Website & creative product designs for brand awareness.', '2021-11-30 07:38:48', '2021-12-07 08:22:06', NULL, 0, '#c9d2ee'),
	(20, 'Global Kidney Foundation', 'projects/November2021/acz9dfg1Tq96zauOYCgE.png', 'projects/November2021/ZvVtPD5TKd42k8iG5H4S.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Development</h1>\r\n<p>The assistance we provided to the U.K based Global Kidney Foundation (GKF) with the ambition to let people get awareness among people in all aspects especially about kidney diseases and organ donations with an informative and creative Website.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/branding">Branding</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'global-kidney-foundation', 'ACTIVE', 'Global Kidney Foundation | Digital Marketing Agency In UK', 'Discover how Global Kidney Foundation made the creative website for public presence.', '2021-11-19 05:08:07', '2022-04-25 13:20:44', NULL, 0, '#ffefeb'),
	(34, 'Halcyon Events', 'projects/December2021/UcrMoRvCjbYHFAsjsMvH.jpg', 'projects/December2021/xX2Ez6vH3fmfsg8IyHAb.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Design &amp; Development</h1>\r\n<p>Halcyon Events is a global house for a broad-pool relationship that are proud of their innovation and creativity in organizing world-class event. They have ground-breaking services to deliver the game changing offerings from festivals, sports events, motorsports events and many others. From Dubai to around the globe, their team of passionate professionals demonstrates great dedication and virtue in the execution process, that touches the human hearts and brains with exceptional touch.</p>\r\n<p>Our Cynosure Designs professionals committed and delivered our client Halcyon Events with an inspirationally designed Website that helped them in achieving their lifelong aspirations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX Designs</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><video class="aligners_work_video" style="object-fit: cover;" poster="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/halcyon-poster.jpg" preload="auto" loop="loop" controls="controls" width="100%">\r\n                    <source src="https://cynosuredesigns.co.uk//storage/projects/videos/formula1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />Sorry, your browser\r\n                    doesn\'t support embedded videos.\r\n                </video></p>', 'halcyon-events', 'ACTIVE', 'Halcyon Events | Digital Marketing Agency In UK | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Halcyon Events made the creative Website and branding for events', '2021-12-24 09:24:01', '2021-12-24 09:44:52', NULL, 0, '#ffe0e0'),
	(35, 'Salamander Brewing Company', 'projects/January2022/VLInkMzqCGjKiczHBf0z.png', 'projects/January2022/hx4gR2IWO5O9DHAEgA57.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Development</h1>\r\n<p>These days beers are everywhere but Salamander Brewing Company is a well-stocked bar of adventurous brews and exciting line-up brewed beers. When in the company of true craft nerds, they will get to choose your own worthwhile glassware. With a massive variety, they continuously evolve in the best breweries and beers that are served in the relaxed environment.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'salamander-brewing-company', 'ACTIVE', 'Salamander Brewing Company | Marketing Agency In UK', 'Discover how Salamander Brewing Company made their Website for seamless user experience and brand awareness.', '2022-01-20 09:36:08', '2022-06-21 04:27:57', NULL, 0, '#b3b2b2'),
	(36, 'School of Business & Management', 'projects/January2022/65k5UyvgbTAVVDgfx2Vg.png', 'projects/January2022/WuLO0ZkZrlzuZMr2LAhV.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Development</h1>\r\n<p>The Malta based SBM is constantly changing everything in the world-consumer perspective. empowering students with professional skills in business and management that is the key to success behind the university. They work hard to make sure that they provide students the opportunities for working with a number of industries and also ensure that their students are well-equipped for the future career.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'school-of-business-and-management', 'ACTIVE', 'School of Business & Management | Digital Marketing Agency', 'Discover how the School of Business & Management made their Website for seamless user experience and brand awareness.', '2022-01-20 10:11:16', '2022-04-26 03:26:44', NULL, 1, '#ffc2c2'),
	(37, 'Anderson Ross', 'projects/January2022/xq53JwiFDyAxhl9J7dEE.png', 'projects/January2022/jKoZWZYRe8BRsWcXuOBW.png', NULL, '<h1>Website Development</h1>\r\n<p>The U.K based Anderson Ross is an award-winning firm, dedicated to help small to large scale businesses in thriving throughout the venture. The company assists in all aspects of business planning, accounts, taxes, VAT, payrolls and many other services. Experienced accountants are available to offer a wide range of value added services to businesses and individuals, all of which can be tailored according to the particular requirements and budget.</p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'anderson-ross', 'ACTIVE', 'Anderson Ross | Digital Marketing Agency In London | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Anderson Rosss made their Website for seamless user experience and brand awareness.', '2022-01-20 10:20:56', '2022-06-21 04:52:33', NULL, 0, '#b6b4ee'),
	(38, 'American Hospital Dubai', 'projects/June2022/ZRXqja7HrO6OlpAtVeYB.png', 'projects/June2022/269EwD70gD9XBoJqysup.webp', NULL, '<p>American Hospital, a renowned private healthcare provider in the Middle East and part of the Mohamed &amp; Obaid Al Mulla Group, was founded in 1996 with the purpose of delivering world-class medical treatments to the community. The team of healthcare professionals specializing in more than 40 medical and surgical disciplines provide comprehensive treatments to patients.</p>\r\n<p>American Hospital also operates dedicated clinics in Dubai Media City, Al Barsha, Al Khawaneej, Jumeirah, Mira, and Dubai Hills, to better serve the community. All physicians at the Hospital are American Board Certified or equivalent, ensuring that patients in the UAE get care that meets global standards. Furthermore, American Hospital became the first medical institution in Dubai to facilitate robotic surgery services, strengthening the Emirate\'s regional position as a hub for medical tourism for patients seeking world-class medical help.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #a00000;">See how we have been helping American Hospital Dubai</span></h3>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/ui-ux-designs">UI/UX Designs</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/software-development">Software Development</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Website Development</h2>\r\n<p>This is true that your website must deliver essential and even vital information if you are in the medical or health sector. Your website must not only look great but also must be easily accessed, user friendly and simple to navigate. Cynosure Design&rsquo;s in-house team designed and developed an innovative Website on the demand of our client, American Hospital Dubai. Our programmers, developers, designers, content writers and video makers dedicatedly produced everything in-house for the website development.</p>\r\n<p>Our specialists delivered American Hospital Dubai, the quality website from start to finish consisting of multiple user friendly functionalities that include setting appointments, finding prospective doctors and services, and location finder.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Moreover the website presents detailed information and guidance about the Departments, packages, branches and more for the community&rsquo;s convenience.</p>\r\n<h3>Key Results:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Established Strong Reputation</li>\r\n<li>Gave 24/7 Online Presence</li>\r\n<li>Understandable Information About Diseases, Symptoms And Treatments</li>\r\n<li>Updated Information About Patient Services And Technologies</li>\r\n<li>Patients Proactively Identified Health Problem</li>\r\n<li>Involved Community And Created Long-Term Loyalty</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Whatsapp Chatbot</h2>\r\n<p>In recent years, hospitals or medical organizations have opted for cutting-edge AI-powered chatbots to assist them in providing the best possible services and treatments to patients. Frequent delays, lack of personalized attention and inefficient patient service are some of the most common issues that patients face and they can be resolved with the help of effective Chatbots.</p>\r\n<p>Cynosure Designs helped American Hospital Dubai with WhatsApp Business API Chatbot that enabled the hospital to gain access to the enormous community in a cost-effective manner. The automated chatbot was designed to rapidly respond to enquiries and concerns from the users all around the world in real time. The WhatsApp chatbot for the AHD was built to better understand user behavior, provide more customized user experience and deliver personalized care to patients. Some of the most used features or use-cases for AHD WhatsApp chatbot include: Symptoms Assessment, Finding the Doctor, Scheduling Appointments, Counseling, Record Keeping, Processing Payments, lab Reports and many more customized options.</p>\r\n<p>As a result, chatbot on WhatsApp helped hospital expand their reach by automating discussions with current and potential users at all hours of the day.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Key Results:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Instant Response To Queries</li>\r\n<li>Speedy And Timely Access To Data</li>\r\n<li>Update On The Care And Treatment Of Patient</li>\r\n<li>Reminders And Notifications To Patients For Ease</li>\r\n<li>24/7 Support Availability</li>\r\n<li>Built A Strong Identity Of Hospital</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Customer Relationship Management (CRM) Software</h2>\r\n<p>Customer retention is becoming one of the most difficult things to maintain in the healthcare sector. The majority of individuals choose a clinic or hospital depending on whether or not the professionals understand their needs and deliver personalized quality of care. As a result, healthcare institutions that lack this critical component are operating at a loss as poor customer service is likely to turn off more potential consumers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This is where a CRM software might help American Hospital Dubai. Cynosure Designs implemented the appropriate tools and technology, required to support shifting trends in marketing and customer relationship management components. We designed a CRM that includes major features such as integrated patient records and the use of electronic data to aid different operations such as the medical history, check-in process, medical billing, patient visits, care and patient management. The automated software provides useful reports for daily analysis of the hospital&rsquo;s work.</p>\r\n<h3>Key Results:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Generated More Leads</li>\r\n<li>Obtaining Business Insights</li>\r\n<li>Keeping Track Of Medical Records</li>\r\n<li>Storing Patient Data</li>\r\n<li>Allocating Resources</li>\r\n<li>Efficiency Enhanced By Automation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We promised to meet the deadlines of American Hospital Dubai and worked with them to deliver up-to-the-mark services at every step of the journey.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'american-hospital-dubai', 'ACTIVE', 'American Hospital Dubai | Digital Marketing Agency In London | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how American Hospital Dubai made its Website for seamless user experience and brand awareness.', '2022-06-20 11:25:23', '2022-06-20 12:51:40', NULL, 1, '#2ec571'),
	(39, 'Continental Tires', 'projects/June2022/pOKwmI4x61ytN2KaKj0p.webp', 'projects/June2022/hyiTFAv1cRCqbfChaHPH.webp', NULL, '<p><strong>Continental Tires</strong> is a German multinational <strong>automobile parts manufacturing company</strong> that specializes in brake systems, interior electronics, automotive safety, engine, tachographs, tires and other parts for the automotive and transportation industry. Continental is the fourth largest tire manufacturer in the world.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #a00000;">Continental is divided into six major divisions:&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Advanced Driver Assistance Systems (Adas)</li>\r\n<li>Tires</li>\r\n<li>Contitech</li>\r\n<li>Chassis And Safety</li>\r\n<li>Powertrain</li>\r\n<li>Interior</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Continental was founded in 1871 in Hannover, Germany and established in the Middle East in 2008 and sold, General Tire, Barum, Matador, Mabor, Semperit, and Uniroyal brands to the countries such as United Arab Emirates, Egypt, Afghanistan, Bahrain, Djibouti, Ethiopia, Iraq, Iran, Jordan, Kuwait, Lebanon, Oman, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, Somalia and Yemen.</p>\r\n<p>Continental sells tires for automobiles, motorcycles, and bicycles worldwide under the Continental brand. Their potential customers include all major automobile, truck and bus producers, such as Porsche, Volkswagen, Toyota, Honda, Daimler AG, Ford, Volvo, Schmitz, Koegel, Freightliner Trucks, BMW, General Motors, Renault and PSA.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #a00000;">See how we have been helping Continental</span></h3>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/digital-marketing/seo">SEO</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/digital-marketing/ppc">PPC</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Website Development</h2>\r\n<p>Continental, the world-renowned automobile parts manufacturing brand opted Cynosure Designs to give their business online presence and showcase their products and services worldwide. We tested and executed plans to sell more automobile parts for Continental, including interior electronics, tachographs, tires and other parts for automotives, best compatible for your automobile.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The goal was to make the website look more updated by using animations, attractive images, cinemagraphs, and unique content. Furthermore, the structure of the website was built for a user-friendly experience while keeping in mind the global brand guidelines and the consumer journey of the target audience. Our digital media agency created and implemented a suitable strategic plan for Continental by giving the website multiregional and bilingual nature.</p>\r\n<p>We made sure that their website delivers a user-friendly responsive website for desktop, smartphones and tablets, while ensuring that the site meets the goals and objectives of the business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #a00000;">Key Results:</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Established Online Brand Identity</li>\r\n<li>Provided A Better First Impression To The Visitors</li>\r\n<li>Boosted Revenues And Profits</li>\r\n<li>Improved Search Rankings</li>\r\n<li>Gained The Competitive Edge</li>\r\n<li>Reduced Bounce Rates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Pay Per Click (PPC) Service&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>In today&rsquo;s modern era businesses advertise to reach their target audience online. When tailored and developed with a clear aim in mind, the ad campaigns may increase brand recognition, generate more leads, and drive sales. To beat this challenge Cynosure Designs outperformed by using the Pay Per Click marketing strategy that put the Continental&rsquo;s business on the fastest track of driving sales. This sales-focused approach proved Continental to be the most cost-effective solution, assuring extremely high return through target marketing.</p>\r\n<p>The PPC campaign not only helped to kick-start a consistent flow of traffic towards Continental automotive website, but also improved the Google ranking. The main benefit our PPC experts gave was the placement of products and services in front of customers online on multiple platforms.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #a00000;">Key Results:</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Increased The Online Visibility</li>\r\n<li>Received More Clicks</li>\r\n<li>Greater Opportunity For Conversions</li>\r\n<li>Contributed Towards Business Goals And Revenues</li>\r\n<li>Improved SEO Performance</li>\r\n<li>More Controlled And Trackable Data</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Search engine Optimization (SEO)</h2>\r\n<p>Today every business is competing to rank better on Search Engine Result Pages (SERP&rsquo;S). Because 85 percent of consumers use search engines to locate the products and services they require, that\'s why it is essential to optimize your website with a sound SEO strategy plan. As optimization leads to increased visibility, more leads generation and eventually increased revenues.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cynosure Designs have tried and tested Continental&rsquo;s automobile parts SEO strategies that are specific to the automotive sector. We\'ve been assisting them in becoming more successful and created a plan to meet the digital marketing demands and objectives. We also provide them a thorough SEO report every month, including the pages, categories, and products we targeted and improved.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #a00000;">Key Results:</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Put Continental At The Top Of The Search Results.</li>\r\n<li>Built Backlinks That Improved Credibility Of Website</li>\r\n<li>Consistent Online Visibility</li>\r\n<li>Built Trust With Customers</li>\r\n<li>Boosted User Experience On The Website</li>\r\n<li>Increased User Engagement And Conversion Rate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a00000;"><strong>Cynosure Designs understood the business goals and objectives that geared towards the boosted Continental\'s conversions and sales.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'continental-tires', 'ACTIVE', 'Continental Tires | Digital Marketing Agency In London | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Continental Tires made its Website for seamless user experience and brand awareness.', '2022-06-21 04:25:11', '2022-06-21 04:51:34', NULL, 1, '#dbdbdb'),
	(40, 'Manakish Oven & Grill', 'projects/June2022/2f2IB3RDxrbRRAPCGBnH.webp', 'projects/June2022/E7Ds59mgRAu8CUWi1xEC.webp', NULL, '<p>Manakish is the elite choice in the restaurants of Walnut Creek, California. Their dominant cuisine highlights Hand-made Bread, Fresh Marinades, and Hand-stretched Cheeses by focusing on excellent tastes and a memorable culinary experience. For them, the most significant aspect of the Manakish experience is the use of fresh ingredients, marinated meats, vegetarian blends with the fresh vegetables. Moreover, they are also providing the exclusive Catering services with the most experienced and qualified chefs that can turn any event into the most memorable moment with the awesome taste of food that everyone can remember for a long time.</p>\r\n<p>Manakish specializes in Mediterranean dishes that include Hummus, Falafel, Zaatar, Fattouh, Fatteh, Kefta and many more that you must like. Serving the ideal meals in addition to sweet delights for friends and family around for well-stocked delicious platters while pleasing themselves with long conversations at the spot.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>They are right here to convey the flavors of Mediterranean food!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #800000;">See how we have been helping Manakish - Oven &amp; Grill</span></h3>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/digital-marketing/seo">SEO</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/digital-marketing/ppc">PPC</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Pay Per Click (PPC) Service</h2>\r\n<p>As we all know, restaurant searches on the internet are popular. To discover the next meal, hungry consumers first look at menus, locations, hours, promotions, reviews, photo galleries, and, most crucially, phone numbers. People search it on their mobile devices and click on Google\'s sponsored ads because they make plans on the go.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Manakish resourced Cynosure Designs to get the most out of conversions and increase the brand awareness around the globe. Our agency tried, tested, and executed successful PPC strategies to raise brand recognition on all paid advertising platforms, including Google Ads, Display Ads, Shopping Feed Ads, Social Media Ads and everything in between. Google AdWords and Google Analytics measure clicks and conversions in real time, allowing us to examine how it is working.</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #800000;">Key Results:</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Moved to Call to Action (CTA)</li>\r\n<li>Optimized the Landing Page</li>\r\n<li>Provided Measurable and Trackable Solution</li>\r\n<li>Enabled Targeting Options</li>\r\n<li>Generated Website Traffic and Sales</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>SEO Service</h2>\r\n<p>We are expert in improving our clients\' search engine results. Our services can assist you in helping your customers to locate your website while looking for the items and services you provide. Our SEO team uses a variety of tools to find the level of search volume that determines how many times a given keyword is searched on Google as Keyword Research is the most crucial tactic in SEO strategy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cynosure Designs helped Manakish to accurately assess the impact of best SEO services and on their restaurant. We gave our client frequent statistics among other things, showing how effective our efforts have been in attracting targeted traffic from search engines and referrals from other websites. We accomplished the purpose and the goal of the website including subscriptions, registrations, order placements, newsletter signups, community involvement and more.</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #800000;">Key Results:</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Boosted Search Rankings</li>\r\n<li>Increased Organic Traffic</li>\r\n<li>Improved Leads and Calls Volume</li>\r\n<li>Elevated Revenues &amp; Profits</li>\r\n<li>Maximum Return on Investment (ROI)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #800000;">Cynosure Designs gave Manakish the online visibility and spread the word about their products and services to the potential customers and on the right platforms!</span></h3>', 'manakish-oven-and-grill', 'ACTIVE', 'Manakish Oven & Grill | Digital Marketing Agency In London | Cynosure Designs', 'Discover how Manakish Oven & Grill made its Website for seamless user experience and brand awareness.', '2022-06-21 04:46:03', '2022-06-21 04:50:14', NULL, 1, '#dbdbdb'),
	(41, 'H & S Security Services', 'projects/July2022/AfCNocg52RxTynTYLyqw.webp', 'projects/July2022/b9awhymk8cHdjH87OOn1.webp', 'H&S Security provides professional security services for their clients across the United Kingdom.', '<p>H&amp;S Security provides professional security services for their clients across the United Kingdom. They have highly trained security guards who have years of experience and training. Their security team is fully licensed and insured, and all guards are background checked and drug tested before they begin working at any of the locations.</p>\r\n<p>H&amp;S Security offers 24/7 service and guarantees a safe environment for corporate clients, community events, and individuals. H&amp;S also offers a training course to individuals to provide an introduction to the fundamentals of security operations. It provides an overview of the various types of threats and trains them with the essential techniques to detect, prevent, respond, and recover from them.</p>\r\n<h3>Services H&amp;S Security Offers:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Manned Guarding</li>\r\n<li>Events Security</li>\r\n<li>Mobile Security Patrol</li>\r\n<li>Key Holding &amp; Alarm Response</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">See how we have been helping H&amp;S Security.</h3>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/digital-marketing/seo">SEO</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Website Development</h2>\r\n<p>People first look at the website when they hear about your business. If you have excellent looking web pages, you will get more customers and sales. Cynosure Designs has proven expertise in creating responsive websites that work across devices. We have built numerous websites using many tools and techniques, knowing what works and what does not.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our team of experts worked closely with H&amp;S Security to understand their business goals and objectives, and then we used our experience to develop a strategy that best matched their brand. We offered various services to H&amp;S Security including web design and development, website SEO, logo design, and content creation. Our approach is simple - we listen, learn and deliver outstanding results.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Key Results:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Established Brand Name</li>\r\n<li>Built Connections With Clients</li>\r\n<li>Generated Organic Traffic</li>\r\n<li>Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO)</li>\r\n<li>24/7 Customer Support Built Trust</li>\r\n<li>Increased Credibility</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Make Your Business Visible Online With Innovative Web Designs!</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'h-and-s-security-services', 'ACTIVE', 'HS Security | Digital Marketing Agency In London', NULL, '2022-07-18 16:36:04', '2022-07-18 16:38:55', NULL, 1, '#cce6ff'),
	(42, 'Red Well Tuition', 'projects/July2022/7ngcvtCDTlJHiUNP2erj.webp', 'projects/July2022/DSVUcWU8ptKUttLJqeVZ.webp', NULL, '<p>Redwell Tuition provides professional tutors who have been certified to teach students at various levels. Their expertise lies in their knowledge of the subject they are teaching. Tutors can be hired anytime to help teach students several subjects, including Maths, English, and Science ranging the stages 1-5. Students can also be prepared for 7+ and 11+ exams, and the tutor&rsquo;s flexible schedule can fit your studies around your busy lifestyle.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">See how we have been helping Redwell Tuition.</h3>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/digital-marketing/seo">SEO</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Website Development</h2>\r\n<p>The role of technology plays an important in the improvement and expansion of education worldwide. Websites are a technology component that allows institutions and individuals to quickly and inexpensively share their profiles and promote them to the rest of the world. Redwell Tuition needed a website that should be easy to navigate and understand where the Users should not need to spend much time searching for the information or trying to figure out what they need to do.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our professional developers accomplished the target by designing and developing a user-friendly website for the client. We created a strategy that focused on providing users with helpful information and engaging them with the content related to tutoring services. The development of the website included web design, logo designing, booking portal, website SEO, and content creation. The website uses responsive web design principles to ensure that the website looks good on any device.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Key Results:</h2>\r\n<ul class="theme_list">\r\n<li>Informative Platform For Students</li>\r\n<li>Saved Time For Students From Searching</li>\r\n<li>Cost-Effective Method To Find Tutors</li>\r\n<li>Online Booking Portal For The Sessions</li>\r\n<li>Enhanced Students&rsquo; Interests</li>\r\n<li>Established Online Visibility</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>A Well-Designed Site Is Not Only Visually Appealing, But It Should Also Be User Friendly!</strong></p>', 'red-well-tuition', 'ACTIVE', 'Redwell Tuition Project | Our Work | Cynosure Designs', 'Cynosure Designs\' professional developers accomplished the target by designing and developing a user-friendly website for Redwell Tuition.', '2022-07-20 12:30:07', '2022-07-20 12:30:07', NULL, 1, '#ffdbdb'),
	(43, 'M4 Facilities Management', 'projects/July2022/dq6J5lCOhUJU7Q7iHRnn.webp', 'projects/July2022/Dn1NuKMVp03OdKLhJOC3.webp', NULL, '<p>M4FM believes they have a unique approach to delivering management facilities services. Their primary goal is to provide tailored quality services to the clients to meet their specific needs as they know that success relies heavily on relationships with the clients and treating them with respect and professionalism by being able to adapt to any situation and respond immediately.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="theme_color">What does M4FM offer?</h3>\r\n<p>M4 provides a range of facilities management services in 4 major domains, including:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Security Services</li>\r\n<li>Facilities Management (FM)</li>\r\n<li>Event Security</li>\r\n<li>Training Solutions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>They provide the services mentioned above in a wide range of sectors; Education, Finance &amp; Insurance, Government, Rail, Leisure &amp; Tourism, Retail, Corporate, Industrial, Transport, and Logistics.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>See how we have been helping M4.</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="project_categories_list pt-2">\r\n<li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/services/digital-marketing/seo">SEO</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Website Development</h2>\r\n<p>The rise of online businesses has led to the creation of dedicated websites to attract more people to their businesses. The websites allow users to create profiles, upload pictures, and videos, and even share information about their products and services.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Every project begins with thorough market research, followed by strategy, creative thinking, and expert execution. Cynosure Designs was opted for the project to create an attractive Website Design for M4 business. We added value by developing an innovative website design focused on capturing user attention and delivering a great user experience. We provided full service to M4 in creating a web design, logo design, graphic design, SEO, content creation, and more. We are passionate about telling stories through our work, and we believe that great ideas start with good visuals. Our clients love working with us because they know they\'ll get a high-quality product at a fair price.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Key Results:</h2>\r\n<ul class="theme_list">\r\n<li>Online Visibility</li>\r\n<li>Brand Awareness</li>\r\n<li>Customized Web Design</li>\r\n<li>Website SEO</li>\r\n<li>Increased Sales Conversion</li>\r\n<li>Better Performance&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>A Digital Agency For The Digital Age To Make Your Website Come Alive!</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'm4-facilities-management', 'ACTIVE', 'M4 Facilities Management Project | Our Work | Cynosure Designs', 'Cynosure Designs was opted for the project to create an attractive Website Design for M4 business that increased Sales Conversion.', '2022-07-20 12:35:17', '2022-07-20 12:37:23', NULL, 1, '#ebffec');
